y 序列化 bug\\n2. 3103 scorer 加 text 字段兼容层\\n3. openclaw-router 判定为半成品，disable systemd service\\n4. 重新配置 cron：wiki-auto-learn 每小时，memory-keeper/memory-maintain 每天\\n5. 实现两层记忆系统：hook 实时写入 ephemeral/ + session-summary LLM 提炼\\n\\n## 重要发现\\n1. 3104 classifier 500 错误根因：numpy.float32 无法 JSON 序列化，修复只需类型转换\\n2. 3103 scorer 只认 prompt 不认 text，gateway hook 发的 text 被忽略\\n3. openclaw-router 核心依赖缺失，不是配置问题，是代码不完整\\n4. 记忆系统评审：总分 3/10，最大问题 context.json 从未被读取\\n5. 两层设计更合理：hook 实时捕获（metadata only）+ session-summary LLM 提炼\\n\\n## 待跟进\\n- [ ] 验证 session-summary 生成摘要文件\\n- [ ] 验证 bootstrap 读取摘要注入新 session\\n- [ ] 确认 ephemeral 内容被正确提炼\\n\\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->\",\"cwd\":\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1776064733378}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"f9c7b560\",\"parentId\":\"5efd6118\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:19:11.339Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The session-summary hook IS working. There's a 2026-04-13-session-summary.md file generated. The chain is:\\n\\n1. ephemeral data is being captured\\n2. session-summary hook is generating summaries\\n3. But the MEMORY.md says the chain was never verified\\n\\nNow let me check if the current session (after /new) is actually picking up this summary. The session started fresh, but did the summary get injected?\\n\\nLet me check the current session context and see if the summary was injected.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"f2b33d166b771ef1baa7cf39e43e490e597c32827f09011ea4e6be846935d7c1\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n部分跑通了——`session-summary` hook 已经生成了摘要（2026-04-13-session-summary.md），ephemeral 数据也在积累。但还没验证的是：**摘要有没有在 /new 后被注入到新 session 的上下文中**。\\n\\n我来测一下：\\n\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_9746dl3tgiud_1\",\"name\":\"sessions_list\",\"arguments\":{\"kinds\":[\"agent\"],\"limit\":5,\"messageLimit\":2}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":3538,\"outpu