{"type":"message","id":"a618846e","parentId":"e1186da4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:20:20.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full transcript. Key observations:\n\n1. There's a `{\"type\":\"session\",...}` entry at the start showing this is a fresh session\n2. Then `{\"type\":\"model_change\"...}`\n3. Then `{\"type\":\"thinking_level_change\"...}`\n4. Then `{\"type\":\"custom\",\"customType\":\"model-snapshot\"...}`\n5. Then `{\"type\":\"message\",...}` - the first user message asking to run session startup sequence\n\nThen after my responses, there's:\n```\n{\"type\":\"custom\",\"customType\":\"openclaw:bootstrap-context:full\",\"data\":{\"timestamp\":1776064647175,\"runId\":\"488d3977-cdad-4389-87f7-bfd679e51a9c\",\"sessionId\":\"d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16\"},\"id\":\"efa38b83\",\"parentId\":\"1cc9d435\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:17:27.175Z\"}\n\n\n```\n\nThis is the bootstrap context injection. But it's happening AFTER my first greeting, not BEFORE. The session started at 07:17:11 and my greeting was at 07:17:27 - so the bootstrap event fired at 07:17:27.175Z, which is after my greeting at 07:17:27.036Z. That's a problem - the bootstrap context was injected after I already sent my greeting, so it didn't influence my initial response.\n\nLooking at the timestamps more carefully, the session began at 07:17:11, my greeting fires at 07:17:27.175Z, and then the bootstrap context arrived at 07:17:27 - so the timing suggests the bootstrap event was triggered but my greeting may have been sent before the bootstrap context was fully processed.\n\n```\n{\"type\":\"custom\",\"customType\":\"openclaw:bootstrap-context:full\",\"data\":{\"timestamp\":1776064647175,\"runId\":\"488d3977-cdad-4389-87f7-bfd679e51a9c\",\"sessionId\":\"d263827d-6dd2-4f5a-84d7-68ae11ee9e16\"},\"id\":\"efa38b83\",\"parentId\":\"1cc9d435\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:17:27.175Z\"}\n```\n\nThis bootstrap event fired at 07:17:27.175Z after my greeting at 07:17:27.036Z, which means the bootstrap context was injected after my initial response rather than before it. The session then continued with the user's question at 07:18:07.\n\nNow I need to examine what bootstrap context was actually injected and verify the session-summary hook behavior. Looking at the session transcript structure, there's a `{\"type\":\"session\",...}` entry followed by model and thinking level changes, then the bootstrap event. My greeting response was generated before the bootstrap was fully processed, so the question is whether bootstrap should have run earlier in the sequence or if this timing is actually correct.\n\nThe real issue seems to be that my greeting didn't reference the session-summary content that should have been available from the bootstrap context injection.\n\nLooking at the session-summary hook, it should write to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary.md` and that file does exist with content from 13:00 UTC. But the bootstrap event timestamp (1776064647175) corresponds to 07:17:11 UTC on April 13, which is exactly when the session started - so the session-summary from the previous session at 13:00 UTC should have been available at session start.\n\nLet me recalculate the conversion: 1776064647175 milliseconds converts to approximately 1776064647 seconds, which when divided by the Unix epoch offset gives me around April 13, 2026 at a specific time.\n\nThe core issue is that bootstrap appears to be firing after my greeting was already sent, which suggests the memory files weren't properly injected during initialization. I should verify whether the session-summary file was actually read and included in the bootstrap context that was delivered before my response.","thinkingSignature":"2c03151f41aac7d3c43432fa4d67f95418a723fc573337e0b020a50eed433809"},{"type":"text","text":"摘要文件是旧的（13:00 UTC），而这个 session 是 07:17 UTC 开始的。关键是看 bootstrap-context-full 事件的内容是否包含 session-summary——我看到 bootstrap 事件在我的第一条回复之后才触发（07:17:27 vs 07:17:11），这个时序有问题。\n\n你说的「上次 session 的记忆」可能是在问这个。这次 /new 触发的是 bootstrap-context 但没读到摘要文件——我得更新 MEMORY.md 把这个链路状态同步一下。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20572,"output":969,"cacheRead":18601,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40142,"cost":{"input":0.006171599999999999,"output":0.0011627999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011160599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00845046}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776064778518,"responseId":"062bcc0de63ea3ec5e53743019b2930f"}}
