r 是实际在跑的任务编排逻辑\n- openclaw-router 是半成品，可以忽略\n- session-summary hook 代码完整，但 bootstrap 注入环节有问题\n- 真正缺的是 bootstrap 能在 session 开始前完成上下文注入\n\n## cron 配置\n\n- wiki-auto-learn: 每小时\n- memory-keeper: 每天 04:00\n- memory-maintain: 每天 03:00\n\n## 待处理\n\n- [ ] 修复 bootstrap-context 时序问题（session-start 应等待 hook）\n- [ ] 验证 session-summary 完整链路\n- [ ] 给 3108 scene-classifier 加 cron 守护"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":827,"cacheRead":18601,"cacheWrite":17094,"totalTokens":36576,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0009924,"cacheRead":0.0011160599999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00641025,"total":0.00853491}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776064847549,"responseId":"062bcc4f0118d7bb376e137c7004e848"}}
