{"type":"message","id":"cdbbe6f8","parentId":"92bb0799","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:26:35.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both versions have the same bug - `top_conf` and `w` are numpy types and are not being converted. The \"fix\" that was mentioned in the ephemeral might have been applied somewhere else or it was the workspace replacement but the bug still exists.\n\nThe fix needs to be applied in both:\n1. `v8/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py` \n2. `workspace/skills/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n\nLet me fix the `scene_classifier.py` to convert numpy types to Python native types. The fix should be applied where the confidence values are put into the return dict.\n\nLet me now fix the v8/scene-classifier version since that's the one being used (running on port 3105).","thinkingSignature":"d1739df6043cc3224ba41d063eea0da58ea2b20dbe05dbc13774858ebda90928"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了——scene-classifier v2 的 numpy.float32 bug 还没修干净。两个版本都有这个问题：`top_conf` 和 `w`（权重）直接返回 numpy 类型，FastAPI 序列化时报错。\n\n修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bf8a8ryhowvb_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py","offset":55,"limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37179,"output":268,"cacheRead":18601,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56048,"cost":{"input":0.011153699999999999,"output":0.0003216,"cacheRead":0.0011160599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01259136}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776065187832,"responseId":"062bcda277d659418efce4209d3cd301"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fb3e2b3","parentId":"cdbbe6f8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:26:35.121Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bf8a8ryhowvb_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \n        vec = self.encoder.encode([text])\n        distances, indices = self.knn.kneighbors(vec)\n        \n        weights = 1 - distances[0]  # cosine距离转相似度\n        top_conf = weights[0]\n        \n        # 构建候选列表\n        candidates = []\n        for idx, w in zip(indices[0], weights):\n            lbl = self.labels[self.label_ids[idx]]\n            candidates.append((lbl, w))\n        \n        # 元判断1：置信度不足\n        if top_conf < self.confidence_threshold:\n            return {\n                \"label\": None,\n                \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n                \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n            }\n        \n        # 元判断2：top2差距过小（歧义）\n        if len(weights) >= 2:\n            gap = weights[0] - weights[1]\n            if gap < self.ambiguity_gap:\n                return {\n                    \"label\": None,\n                    \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n                    \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n                }\n        \n        best_label = candidates[0][0]\n        return {\n            \"label\": best_label,\n            \"confidence\": top_conf,\n            \"meta\": \"confident\",\n            \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n        }\n    \n    def save(self, path):\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(path), exist_ok=True)\n        with open(path, 'wb') as f:\n            pickle.dump({\n                'encoder_name': self.model_name,\n                'labels': self.labels,\n                'label_to_id': self.label_to_id,\n                'embeddings': self.embeddings,\n                'label_ids': self.label_ids,\n                'confidence_threshold': self.confidence_threshold,\n                'ambiguity_gap': self.ambiguity_gap,\n            }, f)\n    \n    @classmethod\n    def load(cls, path):\n        with open(path, 'rb') as f:\n            data = pickle.load(f)\n        \n        obj = cls(model_name=data['encoder_name'])\n\n[13 more lines in file. Use offset=115 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776065195109}}
{"type":"message","id":"0356bd5b","parentId":"3fb3e2b3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:26:53.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to fix the scene_classifier.py to convert numpy types to Python native types. Let me also check the orchestrator's `_log` and `process` methods to make sure all numpy types are handled.\n\nLooking at the code, the bug is in three places where numpy types are returned:\n1. `\"confidence\": top_conf` - needs `float(top_conf)`\n2. `candidates.append((lbl, w))` - needs `float(w)`\n3. `gap = weights[0] - weights[1]` - may also be numpy type\n\nLet me apply the fix to both v8 and workspace versions.","thinkingSignature":"e3085ca05337d8c7909ee845dd305ff8825c7101a230cf91da2381f7ff65b4e6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4jjlysvog801_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py","edits":[{"oldText":"        vec = self.encoder.encode([text])\n        distances, indices = self.knn.kneighbors(vec)\n\n        weights = 1 - distances[0]  # cosine距离转相似度\n        top_conf = weights[0]\n\n        # 构建候选列表\n        candidates = []\n        for idx, w in zip(indices[0], weights):\n            lbl = self.labels[self.label_ids[idx]]\n            candidates.append((lbl, w))\n\n        # 元判断1：置信度不足\n        if top_conf < self.confidence_threshold:\n            return {\n                \"label\": None,\n                \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n                \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n            }\n\n        # 元判断2：top2差距过小（歧义）\n        if len(weights) >= 2:\n            gap = weights[0] - weights[1]\n            if gap < self.ambiguity_gap:\n                return {\n                    \"label\": None,\n                    \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n                    \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n                }\n\n        best_label = candidates[0][0]\n        return {\n            \"label\": best_label,\n            \"confidence\": top_conf,\n            \"meta\": \"confident\",\n            \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n        }","newText":"        vec = self.encoder.encode([text])\n        distances, indices = self.knn.kneighbors(vec)\n\n        weights = 1 - distances[0]  # cosine距离转相似度\n        top_conf = float(weights[0])  # 转换为Python原生类型\n\n        # 构建候选列表\n        candidates = []\n        for idx, w in zip(indices[0], weights):\n            lbl = self.labels[self.label_ids[idx]]\n            candidates.append((lbl, float(w)))  # 转换为Python原生类型\n\n        # 元判断1：置信度不足\n        if top_conf < self.confidence_threshold:\n            return {\n                \"label\": None,\n                \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n                \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n            }\n\n        # 元判断2：top2差距过小（歧义）\n        if len(weights) >= 2:\n            gap = float(weights[0] - weights[1])  # 转换为Python原生类型\n            if gap < self.ambiguity_gap:\n                return {\n                    \"label\": None,\n                    \"confidence\": top_conf,\n                    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n                    \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n                }\n\n        best_label = candidates[0][0]\n        return {\n            \"label\": best_label,\n            \"confidence\": top_conf,\n            \"meta\": \"confident\",\n            \"top_candidates\": candidates[:2]\n        }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37918,"output":871,"cacheRead":18601,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57390,"cost":{"input":0.011375399999999999,"output":0.0010452,"cacheRead":0.0011160599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013536659999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776065195123,"responseId":"062bcdaba20ab3044d9bab01b108b2cb"}}
