{"type":"message","id":"3fe1b7c5","parentId":"0b608705","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:47:11.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the knowledge base situation:\n\n**Current state:**\n1. `memory/entities/` - 49 entity files (active knowledge base)\n2. `memory/knowledge/` - empty directory\n3. `memory/entities-archive/` - archived entities\n4. `memory/raw/` - has docs/notes/papers subdirectories (source material)\n5. `scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py` - exists, last modified Apr 11, but **no cron job** calling it\n6. Multiple wiki scripts: wiki-7h-loop, wiki-7h-loop-v2, wiki-deep-learn-7h, wiki-think-7h - but no active cron\n\n\n7. The LLM Wiki Pattern operates on compile-once rather than RAG principles, and the MEMORY from April 13 claimed wiki-auto-learn was hourly, but that cron job never actually existed. The wiki-auto-learn script itself hasn't been modified since April 11.\n\nThe real cron jobs running are memory-maintain, memory-keeper, and Memory Dreaming Promotion - there's no active wiki learning cycle right now. The system has a solid structure with raw sources feeding into entities and the LLM Wiki Pattern guiding the process, but it's not currently being populated or maintained.","thinkingSignature":"a9102c046b5f5b3e67518fa14da8730413aa6bf732aaadcedf875c40d17247cf"},{"type":"text","text":"知识库现状：\n\n**架构（LLM Wiki 模式）**\n\n```\nraw/ (docs/notes/papers)  →  entities/ (49个)  →  实体页交叉引用\n                                 ↑\n                    session-summary 提炼\n                    ephemeral 捕获碎片\n```\n\n**问题：没有活跃的摄入循环**\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `wiki-auto-learn.py` | 存在，但**无 cron 调用**（最后修改 Apr 11） |\n| `wiki-7h-loop*.sh` | 多个脚本，无 cron |\n| `memory-keeper` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 4 点 |\n| `memory-maintain` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 3 点 |\n| `Memory Dreaming Promo` | ✅ 有 cron，每天 3 点 |\n\nMEMORY 里写的\"wiki-auto-learn 每小时\"是错的——这个 cron 从来没创建过。\n\n**两件事要决定：**\n\n1. **要不要重建 wiki-auto-learn cron？**——基于 `scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py`，每小时扫 raw/ 摄取新文档到 entities/\n2. **还是用 memory-keeper 代替？**——它已经在跑了，可能做了类似的事\n\n要不要我跑一下 `wiki-auto-learn.py` 看看它做什么、效果怎么样？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68066,"output":528,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87308,"cost":{"input":0.0204198,"output":0.0006336,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02217624}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776066410407,"responseId":"062bd26af437eb3515d558afcd0dc81e"}}
