{"type":"message","id":"c70f7d83","parentId":"08c60dcd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:48:45.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the wiki-auto-learn is integrated into the overall framework. They seem surprised/questioning that wiki-auto-learn doesn't have a cron job and isn't part of the main system.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The user's question \"没进入整体框架吗？\" means \"It's not integrated into the overall framework?\"\n\nLooking at what we know:\n1. `wiki-auto-learn.py` exists as a script but has no cron\n2. `memory-keeper`, `memory-maintain`, `Memory Dreaming Promo` are the three active crons\n3. The ephemeral → session-summary → bootstrap chain is the \"two-layer memory system\"\n\n\n4. The wiki knowledge base appears to be a separate system that was built but never connected to the main cron jobs\n\nSo the real issue is that the wiki ingestion pipeline exists in isolation—it's not wired into any of the active scheduled tasks or the bootstrap memory chain. I need to figure out whether the user wants me to integrate it into the existing framework or if they want a completely different approach.","thinkingSignature":"b7a74010115f8f3af9e7471a0bb61da75425d9f44b5be612d657fc25c6105745"},{"type":"text","text":"没有。从来没进框架。\n\n现在的框架只有三层：\n\n```\nephemeral (捕获)\n    ↓ hook\nsession-summary (提炼)      ← 每隔一段时间 summary hook 做一次\n    ↓ bootstrap hook 注入\n新 session 上下文\n```\n\n而 wiki-auto-learn 是一个独立的 Python 脚本，没人调用它，没有任何调度。它跟上面的框架完全平行、不相交。\n\n**这说明之前的实现是散的**：做了很多工具脚本，但没有纳入 cron 体系，也没有和 session-summary / ephemeral 链路打通。\n\n如果要让知识库进入框架，有两种接法：\n\n| 方案 | 做法 | 改动量 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| A. 接到 memory-keeper | 让 keeper 在跑的时候顺便调 wiki-auto-learn | 小 |\n| B. 接到 session-summary | hook 每次 session 结束时顺便触发一次 wiki 摄取 | 中 |\n| C. 新建 cron | 每小时跑一次 wiki-auto-learn | 小，但有重复调度 |\n\n你倾向哪种？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":416,"cacheRead":84290,"cac