{"type":"message","id":"0b0192a8","parentId":"156d78ed","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:43.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Set up the wiki-auto-learn cron job\n2. Make sure the whole framework runs through properly\n\nLet me first check the wiki-auto-learn.py script to understand what it does and what parameters it needs. Then I'll create a cron job for it.\n\nLet me also think about what \"整个框架跑通\" means:\n1. ephemeral captures events ✅ (already working)\n2. session-summary hook generates summaries ✅ (already working)\n3. bootstrap hook injects summaries into new sessions ✅ (just fixed)\n4. wiki-auto-learn cron - needs to be set up\n5. memory-keeper/memory-maintain - already have cron entries\n\n\n6. Need to examine the wiki-auto-learn.py script to see what arguments it accepts and how to properly configure it for the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"400cfed86d61a84c5d369b596ca4024b9be15d248f80509063959c0c1eafcf51"},{"type":"text","text":"先摸清楚 wiki-auto-learn.py 的用法：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tzzatbevsv3j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py","offset":40,"limit":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":234,"cacheRead":87586,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87874,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0002808,"cacheRead":0.005255159999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0055521599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066687856,"responseId":"062bd380af6b72e8c79a73c8bda3decb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c21a9c18","parentId":"0b0192a8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:43.809Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tzzatbevsv3j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/\n        skills_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/skills\")\n        if skills_dir.exists():\n            for f in skills_dir.iterdir():\n                if f.is_dir():\n                    sources.append((\"skill\", str(f)))\n        \n        return sources\n    \n    def synthesize(self, source):\n        \"\"\"2. 思考合成 (Synthesize) - 对照原文核心\"\"\"\n        source_type, source_path = source\n        name = Path(source_path).name\n        \n        # 对照 LLM Wiki 原文核心\n        analysis = {\n            \"name\": name,\n            \"type\": source_type,\n            \"value\": \"unknown\",\n            \"relevance\": \"unknown\",\n            \"action\": \"skip\"\n        }\n        \n        # 根据原文：知识是否与现有 wiki 相关？\n        # 是否值得编译到 wiki？\n        # 是否能增强现有实体页？\n        \n        # 简单判断：与 OpenClaw、Claude Code、Skills 相关则入\n        keywords = [\"claude\", \"code\", \"openclaw\", \"skill\", \"tool\", \"agent\"]\n        if any(k in name.lower() for k in keywords):\n            analysis[\"value\"] = \"high\"\n            analysis[\"action\"] = \"ingest\"\n        \n        return analysis\n    \n    def write_back(self, analysis):\n        \"\"\"3. 写回 (Write-back)\"\"\"\n        if analysis[\"action\"] != \"ingest\":\n            return False\n        \n        # 根据原文：更新实体页、索引、log\n        # 一个 source 最多可影响 10-15 页\n        \n        # 检查是否已有对应实体页\n        entity_name = analysis[\"name\"].lower().replace(\".md\", \"\").replace(\" \", \"-\")\n        entity_file = Path(ENTITIES_DIR) / f\"{entity_name}.md\"\n        \n        if not entity_file.exists():\n            # 创建新实体页\n            content = f\"\"\"---\ntitle: {analysis['name']}\ntype: entity\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}\ntags: [auto, {analysis['type']}]\n---\n\n# {analysis['name']}\n\n> 自动从 {analysis['type']} 摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: {analysis['type']}\n- 路径: {analysis['name']}\n- 摄入时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')}\n\n## 分析\n\n基于 LLM Wiki 原文分析：\n- 价值评估: {analysis['value']}\n- 相关性: {analysis['relevance']}\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[llm-wiki]] - LLM Wiki 模式\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 如何使用\n\"\"\"\n            entity_file.write_text(content, encoding='utf-8')\n            self.log(f\"  📝 创建实体页: {entity_name}\")\n\n[110 more lines in file. Use offset=140 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776066703797}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee8cc0cd","parentId":"c21a9c18","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:48.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me see the rest of the file, especially how it's invoked from command line (if at all) and what arguments it takes.","thinkingSignature":"9783d767c4df882a205401c40f3c2855d27a9da29b56b0956743bd5b1026a5de"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rq4o25t0k5c1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py","offset":140,"limit":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69922,"output":86,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88722,"cost":{"input":0.020976599999999998,"output":0.0001032,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02220264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066703812,"responseId":"062bd38f0a520d06376473845342007d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"047d754b","parentId":"ee8cc0cd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:48.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rq4o25t0k5c1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            return True\n        \n        return False\n    \n    def lint_check(self):\n        \"\"\"4. Lint 检查\"\"\"\n        issues = {\n            \"dead_links\": [],\n            \"orphans\": [],\n            \"stale\": []\n        }\n        \n        # 死链检查\n        entity_files = list(Path(ENTITIES_DIR).glob(\"*.md\"))\n        all_links = set()\n        \n        for ef in entity_files:\n            content = ef.read_text(encoding='utf-8')\n            # 提取 [[link]] 格式\n            links = re.findall(r'\\[\\[([a-z0-9-]+)\\]\\]', content)\n            all_links.update(links)\n        \n        # 检查死链\n        for link in all_links:\n            if not (Path(ENTITIES_DIR) / f\"{link}.md\").exists():\n                issues[\"dead_links\"].append(link)\n        \n        # 修复死链\n        for dl in issues[\"dead_links\"]:\n            # 简单处理：移除死链引用\n            for ef in entity_files:\n                content = ef.read_text(encoding='utf-8')\n                new_content = content.replace(f\"[[{dl}]]\", \"\")\n                if new_content != content:\n                    ef.write_text(new_content, encoding='utf-8')\n                    self.log(f\"  🔧 修复死链: {dl}\")\n        \n        return issues\n    \n    def run_cycle(self, cycle_num):\n        \"\"\"执行一个完整循环\"\"\"\n        self.stats[\"iterations\"] += 1\n        \n        # 1. Ingest - 扫描新知识\n        sources = self.scan_sources()\n        \n        # 2. Synthesize - 思考每个源\n        ingested_count = 0\n        for source in sources:\n            analysis = self.synthesize(source)\n            if self.write_back(analysis):\n                ingested_count += 1\n                self.stats[\"ingested\"] += 1\n        \n        # 3. Lint - 检查健康\n        issues = self.lint_check()\n        fixed = len(issues[\"dead_links\"])\n        self.stats[\"fixed\"] += fixed\n        \n        # 4. 记录到 log (符合原文格式)\n        self._append_log(cycle_num, sources, issues)\n        \n        # 输出状态\n        self.log(f\"  循环 {cycle_num}: 扫描 {len(sources)} 个源, \"\n                f\"摄入 {ingested_count} 个, 修复 {fixed} 个死链\")\n        \n        return {\n            \"sources\": len(sources),\n            \"ingested\": ingested_count,\n            \"fixed\": fixed,\n            \"dead_links\": len(issues[\"dead_links\"])\n        }\n    \n    def _append_log(self, cycle, sources, issues):\n        \"\"\"追加到 log.md (符合原文格式)\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n        entry = f\"\\n## [{timestamp}] auto-cycle | iter {cycle} | sources:{len(sources)} | fixed:{len(issues['dead_links'])}\"\n        \n        with open(LOG_FILE, \"a\", encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            f.write(entry)\n    \n    def run(self, duration_minutes=420, interval_seconds=120):\n        \"\"\"运行自动化循环\"\"\"\n        cycles = (duration_minutes * 60) // interval_seconds\n        \n        self.log(f\"=== 启动 {duration_minutes} 分钟自动化学习循环 ===\")\n        self.log(f\"周期: {interval_seconds}秒, 总循环: {cycles} 次\")\n        self.log(f\"核心原则: {CORE_PRINCIPLES}\")\n        \n        for i in range(1, cycles + 1):\n            try:\n                result = self.run_cycle(i)\n                \n                # 进度\n                percent = int(i * 100 / cycles)\n                print(f\"[PROGRESS] {percent}% | {i}/{cycles} | ing:{result['ingested']} fix:{result['fixed']}\")\n                \n            except Exception as e:\n                self.log(f\"  ❌ 错误: {e}\")\n                self.stats[\"errors\"] += 1\n            \n            time.sleep(interval_seconds)\n        \n        self.log(f\"=== 循环完成 ===\")\n        self.log(f\"统计: {self.stats}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    wiki = WikiAutoLearn()\n    wiki.run(duration_minutes=420, interval_seconds=120)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776066708417}}
{"type":"message","id":"2de2fc1a","parentId":"047d754b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:56.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script is designed to run as a long loop (420 minutes = 7 hours, with 120 second intervals). It doesn't take command line arguments for a one-shot run.\n\nFor cron use, I need to either:\n1. Modify the script to support one-shot mode\n2. Create a wrapper that runs a single cycle\n\nThe script's `run_cycle()` method does exactly what we want - scans sources, synthesizes, writes back, and does lint check. The `run()` method just wraps it in a loop.\n\nFor cron, we want it to run once per trigger. Let me check if there's a simpler script for single runs, like `wiki-trigger.sh`.","thinkingSignature":"61f2090c61abfd8a1c1ae4712be912089fa91683fea7158c317d7e2f6dc1098c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gx7f93sn4d1s_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-trigger.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":70932,"output":175,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89821,"cost":{"input":0.0212796,"output":0.00020999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022612439999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066708429,"responseId":"062bd3930250e8f73d690d8e4e4d1ef2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ffb4f790","parentId":"2de2fc1a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:51:56.301Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gx7f93sn4d1s_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki 自动触发机制\n# 当满足条件时自动执行操作\n\nENTITIES=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\nLOG=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log.md\"\n\n# 触发条件配置\nMAX_ORPHANS=3\nMAX_DEAD=0\n\n# 检查函数\ncheck_health() {\n    local orphans=0 dead=0\n    \n    for f in $ENTITIES/*.md; do\n        fname=$(basename \"$f\" .md)\n        [ $(grep -r \"\\[\\[$fname\\]\\]\" $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l) -eq 0 ] && orphans=$((orphans+1))\n    done\n    \n    for link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' $ENTITIES/*.md | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n        [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ] || dead=$((dead+1))\n    done\n    \n    echo \"$orphans $dead\"\n}\n\n# 执行检查\nread orphans dead <<< $(check_health)\n\n# 触发动作\nif [ $orphans -gt $MAX_ORPHANS ] || [ $dead -gt $MAX_DEAD ]; then\n    echo \"[$(date)] 触发 Lint: orphans=$orphans dead=$dead\"\n    /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh >> $LOG\nelse\n    echo \"[$(date)] 健康: orphans=$orphans dead=$dead\"\nfi\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776066716289}}
{"type":"message","id":"a51adf08","parentId":"ffb4f790","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:52:00.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `wiki-trigger.sh` runs health checks and triggers `auto-lint.sh` if needed, but it doesn't run `wiki-auto-learn.py`. \n\nThe `wiki-auto-learn.py` is designed to run as a long 7-hour loop, not as a one-shot. For cron use, I need to adapt it.\n\nOptions:\n1. Create a wrapper that runs a single cycle of wiki-auto-learn\n2. Modify wiki-auto-learn.py to support a `--once` flag\n3. Use the existing `wiki-7h-loop.sh` or `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` scripts\n\nLet me check `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` to see if it's more suitable for cron use.","thinkingSignature":"8f4ba0d0c6168860c4d9e16b615a36950c7002fce260153d86dc260d7cd8ff03"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_od627qxzn315_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71462,"output":190,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90366,"cost":{"input":0.0214386,"output":0.00022799999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022789439999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066716305,"responseId":"062bd39aa6fae635a50016fe3dd90959"}}
{"type":"message","id":"80c24a30","parentId":"a51adf08","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:52:01.065Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_od627qxzn315_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# LLM Wiki 7小时自动化学习循环 (修正版)\n# 贯彻需求 + LLM Wiki 原文\n# 区分: skills/ → 实体页 | docs/ → Raw Sources\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nCOUNTER=0\nMAX_ITERATIONS=210  # 7小时\n\necho \"=== 7小时自动化学习循环启动 (修正版) ===\"\necho \"开始: $(date)\"\necho \"规则: skills/→实体页, docs/→Raw Sources\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 确保 raw 目录存在\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\nwhile [ $COUNTER -lt $MAX_ITERATIONS ]; do\n    COUNTER=$((COUNTER + 1))\n    PERCENT=$((COUNTER * 100 / MAX_ITERATIONS))\n    MINUTE=$((COUNTER * 2))\n    \n    echo \"[$(date +%H:%M:%S)] 循环 $COUNTER/$MAX_ITERATIONS\"\n    \n    # ===== 1. Ingest - 扫描知识源 =====\n    # 只扫描 skills/ 目录创建实体页 (不是 docs/)\n    NEW_ENTITIES=0\n    \n    for skill in $WORKSPACE/skills/*/; do\n        if [ -d \"$skill\" ]; then\n            name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n            # 检查是否已有实体页且不在归档中\n            if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ]; then\n                # 创建实体页\n                cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动摄入的技能\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 如何使用\nEOF\n                echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n                NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    # 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources (不创建实体页)\n    DOCS_COUNT=$(ls $WORKSPACE/docs/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    if [ $DOCS_COUNT -gt 0 ]; then\n        echo \"  📂 Raw Sources: $DOCS_COUNT 个文档\"\n    fi\n    \n    # ===== 2. Synthesize - 思考 (对照 LLM Wiki 原文核心) =====\n    echo \"  🧠 思考: 对照原文 - 增量构建、编译一次、持续更新\"\n    \n    # ===== 3. Write-back =====\n    WRITTEN=$NEW_ENTITIES\n    \n    # ===== 4. Lint - 死链检查与修复 =====\n    FIXED=0\n    for link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n        if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n            # 自动修复：移除死链\n            sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null\n            FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    if [ $FIXED -gt 0 ]; then\n        echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n    fi\n    \n    # ===== 5. 记录 log =====\n    ENTITY_COUNT=$(ls $ENTITIES/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    echo \"## [$(date +%Y-%m-%d\\ %H:%M)] auto-cycle | iter $COUNTER | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$WRITTEN | fixed:$FIXED\" >> $LOG\n    \n    # 进度输出\n    echo \"  ✅ 实体页:$ENTITY_COUNT | 新增:$WRITTEN | 修复:$FIXED\"\n    echo \"[PROGRESS] ${PERCENT}% | $COUNTER/$MAX_ITERATIONS | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT\"\n    echo \"---\"\n    \n    # 等待 2 分钟\n    sleep 120\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 7小时循环完成 ===\"\necho \"结束: $(date)\""}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776066721056}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a4a5d48","parentId":"80c24a30","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:52:32.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` is a long-running 7-hour loop (210 iterations × 2 minutes = 420 minutes = 7 hours). This is NOT suitable for cron use because:\n1. It runs for 7 hours straight\n2. It would overlap with the next cron trigger\n\nFor cron use, I need a **one-shot version** that runs a single cycle quickly and exits. Let me look at what a single cycle does:\n1. Scan skills/ - create entity pages for new skills\n2. Scan docs/ - count raw sources\n3. Check for dead links\n4. Log\n\n\nA single cycle would probably finish in under a second. I should create a lightweight one-shot cron script that handles skills/ → entity pages, docs/ → raw sources counting, dead link checking, and logging without the long-running loop. I'll call it `wiki-learn-once.sh` and set it to run hourly via cron. The existing `wiki-auto-learn.py` is too heavy for this since it's designed for continuous long-running cycles, so I need to build something purpose-built for hourly cron execution.","thinkingSignature":"a03580664acc28deabe40bda13bc5699c685982f9af2c9abb9987a079f2d14ca"},{"type":"text","text":"理解了。`wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` 是 7 小时长循环，不适合 cron。需要一个**一次跑完**的版本。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0l1kj7nfjjwa_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 每次运行一个完整 cycle：扫描 → 摄取 → 写回 → Lint\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 1. Ingest: 扫描 skills/ 创建实体页 =====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    if [ -d \"$skill\" ]; then\n        name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n        if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ]; then\n            cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n            echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n            NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nPAPERS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.pdf 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 2. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ $FIXED -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 3. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn-once | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED | docs:$DOCS_COUNT\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72669,"output":1041,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92424,"cost":{"input":0.0218007,"output":0.0012492,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024172739999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066721069,"responseId":"062bd3a265a37594129c1726841cf6aa"}}
