{"type":"message","id":"1b3f932d","parentId":"634e3608","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:58:48.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So we have:\n- 7 claude-code report files to archive\n- 3 duplicates: task-orchestrator + task_orchestrator, v8-scorer + v8_classifier + v8_scorer, and I need to check v8-classifier too\n- 16 auto-ingested skill pages (except v8_classifier/v8_scorer which are in both categories)\n\nThat's 7 + (3 duplicates = 3 files, keep the hyphenated ones) + 14 unique auto-ingested = 24 to archive. \n\nAfter archiving: 66 - 24 = 42. Still above 30.\n \nI'm realizing the deduplication alone won't get us down to 30—I'd need to archive around 36 files total. If I archive all the auto-ingested ones, that's still only about 31 files, leaving us at 35, which is closer but not quite there.\n\nThe real opportunity is consolidating those 7 claude-code report files into a single master document, which would save 6 files and get us closer to the target. I'll write a pruning script that handles the straightforward archiving and deduplication first, then tackle the claude-code consolidation separately if needed.","thinkingSignature":"29259ce5a235ca39788398abad5ce2b33ce64af61d5c8ed15de778d718da8fa6"},{"type":"text","text":"策略：归档 7 个 claude-code 报告（合并成 1 个）+ 合并 3 组重复 + 移出 14 个低优先级 auto-ingested skill。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3j144c6lwpr8_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/entity-prune.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Entity 精简脚本：归档报告合并 + 去重 + 清理低优先级\n# 目标：entities/ 保持在 30 个左右\n\nENTITIES=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\nARCHIVE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive\"\nTODAY=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\n\nmkdir -p \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$TODAY] === Entity 精简开始 ===\"\n\n# 1. 合并 claude-code 报告 (7个 → 1个)\nREPORT_FILES=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/claude-code-*-report*.md 2>/dev/null)\nif [ -n \"$REPORT_FILES\" ]; then\n    echo \"  📄 合并 claude-code 报告...\"\n    # 保留最后一个（最完整），其余归档\n    for f in $REPORT_FILES; do\n        fname=$(basename \"$f\")\n        if [ \"$fname\" = \"claude-code-final-ultimate-complete-report.md\" ]; then\n            # 重命名为通用报告\n            mv \"$f\" \"$ENTITIES/claude-code-reports.md\"\n            echo \"  ✅ 保留: claude-code-reports.md\"\n        else\n            mv \"$f\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n            echo \"  📦 归档: $fname\"\n        fi\n    done\nfi\n\n# 2. 去重：下划线版本 vs 横线版本（保留横线版本）\nfor DUP in task_orchestrator v8_scorer v8_classifier; do\n    UNDERSCORE=\"$ENTITIES/${DUP}.md\"\n    HYPHEN=\"${DUP//_/-}.md\"\n    if [ -f \"$UNDERSCORE\" ] && [ -f \"$ENTITIES/$HYPHEN\" ]; then\n        echo \"  🔗 去重: ${DUP} → $HYPHEN (保留)\"\n        mv \"$UNDERSCORE\" \"$ARCHIVE/$(basename $UNDERSCORE)\"\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 3. 清理低优先级 auto-ingested skills（已在上一轮从 skills/ 目录摄入，跳过）\n# 仅当 entity 是纯 auto-ingested 且无实质内容时移出\nfor ENTITY in automation-workflows classifier-health critical-interceptor \\\n              intent-enhancer multi-search-engine ontology proactivity \\\n              productivity-automation-kit scrapling superpowers \\\n              memory-keeper elite-longterm-memory github-manager \\\n              vercel-deploy; do\n    FILE=\"$ENTITIES/${ENTITY}.md\"\n    if [ -f \"$FILE\" ]; then\n        # 检查是否只有自动生成的模板内容（无实质洞察）\n        LINES=$(wc -l < \"$FILE\")\n        if [ \"$LINES\" -lt 25 ]; then\n            mv \"$FILE\" \"$ARCHIVE/${ENTITY}.md\"\n            echo \"  🗑  移出(空模板): $ENTITY.md (${LINES}行)\"\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 统计\nCOUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  ✅ 精简完成: entities/ 现在 $COUNT 个\"\n\n# 4. 输出保留清单\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 当前 entities/ ($COUNT 个) ===\"\nls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md | xargs -n1 basename | sort\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":76541,"output":1036,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96291,"cost":{"input":0.022962299999999998,"output":0.0012431999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cac