{"type":"message","id":"85d72a07","parentId":"1a18392a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:59:37.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"32个，接近目标30个。现在需要把 entity-prune.sh 整合到 wiki-learn cron 或者 memory-keeper 里，让它定期运行。\n\n但 entity-prune.sh 里有 hardcoded 逻辑（比如判断22行以下的都是空模板），更适合加到 memory-keeper 或者让 wiki-learn 跑完之后自动触发一次 prune。\n\n或者更简单：直接在 wiki-learn-once.sh 末尾加一行调用 entity-prune.sh，这样每次新 entity 入库时自动精简。\n\n但这样会有问题：如果每次 wiki-learn 都触发 prune，那些刚入库的17个 skill 实体每次都会被移出（因为它们只有22行）。\n\n\n最合理的方案是让 entity-prune 独立运行，作为 memory-maintain 的一部分，或者用 cron 定期触发。在 wiki-learn 的末尾调用它也行，只要确保不会每次都把新入库的内容删掉。需要在脚本里加个保护机制，比如按时间戳判断，避免刚入库的内容被误删。\n\n实际上 wiki-learn-once.sh 每次扫 skills/ 时，已经入库的会跳过不重复创建，所以不会产生新的22行文件。但 prune 每次跑都会把22行以下的移出，包括之前已经入住的。\n\n关键问题是：如果 wiki-learn 后续某个 skill 产生了实质内容被写入了，那个文件就不再是22行，prune 就不会误删它。这个设计其实是可以工作的。\n\n不过 prune 脚本本身还有问题——它是直接移出文件到 archive，而不是删除，所以 archive 会一直膨胀。为了让 prune 定期运行并真正减少实体数量，我应该把 entity-prune.sh 整合到 wiki-learn-once.sh 末尾作为调用，或者让它接受一个参数来控制保留实体的最小行数。\n\n考虑到 archive 已经有 152+ 个文件了，prune 不需要每次都清理所有低优先级内容，只要控制 entities/ 总数在 30 左右就行。\n\n最直接的方法是修改 wiki-learn-once.sh，让它在每次运行时都执行 prune，这样每小时自动调用一次，entities/ 的数量就会被自动控制住。","thinkingSignature":"e26e29c9e08873decdf7f71687fbe0c4c2d13c27b774635580bb741bacd04238"},{"type":"text","text":"32个，在目标附近了。把 prune 整合进 wiki-learn-once.sh，每次摄入后自动精简：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6zumox22wrlh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79426,"output":467,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98607,"cost":{"input":0.0238278,"output":0.0005604,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02551104}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067157693,"responseId":"062bd554bfbb2e2d16acea82d9a65299"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e95c4c96","parentId":"85d72a07","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:59:37.783Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6zumox22wrlh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 每次运行一个完整 cycle：扫描 → 摄取 → 写回 → Lint\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 1. Ingest: 扫描 skills/ 创建实体页 =====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    if [ -d \"$skill\" ]; then\n        name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n        if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ]; then\n            cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n            echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n            NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nPAPERS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.pdf 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 2. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ $FIXED -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 3. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn-once | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED | docs:$DOCS_COUNT\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776067177772}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a627ef4","parentId":"e95c4c96","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:59:54.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to add an auto-prune step at the end that:\n1. Only archives entities that have been \"auto-ingested\" AND have low content (under ~25 lines)\n2. Never archives manually created/curated entities (which have status: curated or don't have auto-ingested tag)\n3. Protects entities that have been enriched with real content beyond the template\n\nLet me design a smarter prune. The key insight is:\n- Auto-ingested entities have `status: auto-ingested` in their frontmatter\n- Curated/manual entities don't have this tag\n- Only prune `status: auto-ingested` entities that are still \"thin\" (under ~25 lines)\n\n\n- This way I won't accidentally remove entities that were auto-ingested first but later enriched with meaningful content.\n\nNow I'll write a prune step to add to wiki-learn-once.sh that only removes auto-ingested entities with minimal content.","thinkingSignature":"d256b705b1b1473d34a555b87e9a32cd8ac39028d03596e7c3ff7f0f57de5c73"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kl75m12mpaje_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"# ===== 3. 记录 log =====","newText":"# ===== 3. Auto-prune: 保持 entities 在 30 个左右 =====\nPRUNED=0\nTARGET=35  # 超过此数才触发 prune\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt \"$TARGET\" ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 Auto-prune: 当前 $CURRENT 个，超过目标 $TARGET\"\n    ARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\n    mkdir -p \"$ARCHIVE\"\n    \n    # 策略：只移出 status:auto-ingested 且行数少于25行的\"空模板\"\n    for f in \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md; do\n        [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n        fname=$(basename \"$f\")\n        \n        # 检查是否有 auto-ingested 标记且内容单薄\n        if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n            lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n            if [ \"$lines\" -lt 25 ]; then\n                mv \"$f\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n                PRUNED=$((PRUNED + 1))\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    [ \"$PRUNED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🗑  Auto-prune 移出: $PRUNED 个空模板\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 4. 记录 log ====="}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80635,"output":598,"cacheRead":18714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99947,"cost":{"input":0.0241905,"output":0.0007176,"cacheRead":0.00112284,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02603094}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067177785,"responseId":"062bd569b6e035d026e2c2750b321390"}}
