{"type":"message","id":"58bae5ff","parentId":"66e82c9b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:07:37.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out that if a new skill entity gets added (like the 17 that were added today), the count goes above 35, triggering the auto-prune. But auto-prune only removes `status: auto-ingested` entries. So if a new real entity is added (one that's valuable), it won't be pruned. But then the count would still stay above 35 if we keep adding...\n\nWait, the user's concern is different. Let me think:\n\n1. Current count: 32\n2. If cron runs and adds new entities, it could go to 33, 34, 35...\n3. Once it exceeds 35, auto-prune kicks in\n\n\n4. Auto-prune removes `status: auto-ingested` entries with fewer than 25 lines, which would free up space but also potentially remove the newly added empty entities\n\nThe real issue is that cron runs hourly and keeps adding new entities, triggering the prune cycle repeatedly—new entities get added, then removed when the count exceeds the threshold. This creates an unstable loop where the system keeps pruning without ever stabilizing around the target size. A 24-hour cooling-off period after pruning would prevent this thrashing. to 35, prunes 1 entry, count = 34\n- Good, stable at 34\n\nBut the user's concern might be: what if the entities that get pruned are the newly added ones (the 17 that were just added are all status:auto-ingested)? Then it would be a cat-and-mouse game.\n\nThe better approach: instead of just pruning when over 35, we should have a smarter system that:\n1. Tracks which entities are \"important\" (manually created or referenced often) vs \"disposable\" (auto-ingested empty ones)\n2. Only prunes disposable ones\n3. When count goes over target, prune down to target-5 (give buffer room)\n\nOr better yet: instead of the cron adding entities (which creates this loop), the auto-prune should run as a **separate** maintenance task, not as part of the learn cycle.\n\nActually, I think the user's concern is simpler: every hour, new entities get added and could exceed the 30-35 limit. The current pruning logic only removes entries that are both auto-ingested and short. If all the auto-ingested entries have already been pruned away but new ones keep getting added, the count could still balloon beyond the target. The real problem is that adding new entities is decoupled from the pruning logic—they happen in sequence, so we could add several new ones before pruning kicks in again.\n\nThe better approach would be to check the entity count before adding new ones and prune first if needed, or set the threshold lower (like 30) to give more buffer room. But I think the simplest fix is to just be more aggressive with the pruning—prune down to 25 instead of just removing one entry, so there's more cushion before the next cycle. The user's main concern is that we're adding entities at the same time we're trying to prune them. The real issue is that we need to prune based on actual value, not just auto-ingested status—manually created high-value entities should stay, while new auto-ingested ones that are empty should be the first to go when we're over the limit. A smarter approach would be to sort by a \"disposability score\" (prioritizing status:auto-ingested and low line count) and remove from the bottom up whenever we exceed the threshold, but I think the quickest fix is just adjusting the threshold to 25 with aggressive pruning down to 20 to keep a comfortable buffer.","thinkingSignature":"550f3b3464a249ce7f972561f7b82b223ab0b8cf6e01668e9225b137b5efd05e"},{"type":"text","text":"问得好。当前逻辑有漏洞——auto-prune 只在超过 35 时触发，只删 auto-ingested 空模板。如果新增的都是空模板，删了又加、加了又删，循环。\n\n改成：**先检查空间，不够就清理再添加，并且按\"最可丢弃\"排序删**。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5qij9x1x492i_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":845,"cacheRead":99442,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100341,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.001014,"cacheRead":0.0059665199999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00699672}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067616613,"responseId":"062bd721febab8e4687227019e7b6f14"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad655762","parentId":"58bae5ff","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:07:37.667Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5qij9x1x492i_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 每次运行一个完整 cycle：扫描 → 摄取 → 写回 → Lint\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 1. Ingest: 扫描 skills/ 创建实体页 =====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    if [ -d \"$skill\" ]; then\n        name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n        if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ]; then\n            cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n            echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n            NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nPAPERS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.pdf 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 2. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ $FIXED -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 3. Auto-prune: 保持 entities 在 30 个左右 =====\nPRUNED=0\nTARGET=35  # 超过此数才触发 prune\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt \"$TARGET\" ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 Auto-prune: 当前 $CURRENT 个，超过目标 $TARGET\"\n    ARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\n    mkdir -p \"$ARCHIVE\"\n    \n    # 策略：只移出 status:auto-ingested 且行数少于25行的\"空模板\"\n    for f in \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md; do\n        [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n        fname=$(basename \"$f\")\n        \n        # 检查是否有 auto-ingested 标记且内容单薄\n        if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n            lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n            if [ \"$lines\" -lt 25 ]; then\n                mv \"$f\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n                PRUNED=$((PRUNED + 1))\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n    \n    [ \"$PRUNED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🗑  Auto-prune 移出: $PRUNED 个空模板\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 4. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn-once | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED | docs:$DOCS_COUNT\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776067657643}}
