{"type":"message","id":"615b2dbd","parentId":"9eaf6ca8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:08:32.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me rewrite the auto-prune logic to be smarter:\n\n1. **Space budget**: Before adding new entities, calculate how much room we have (TARGET - current)\n2. **Smart ordering**: Sort candidates by disposability - auto-ingested + fewer lines = more disposable\n3. **Prune first, then add**: Make space before adding, not after\n4. **Buffer**: Target 28 (so we can absorb 2 hours of additions before next prune)\n\nActually, the cleanest approach:\n- TARGET = 30\n- Before adding new entities: check if current + new > TARGET + buffer\n- If so, prune first (sort by disposability: auto-ingested first, then by line count ascending)\n\n\n- Then add\n\nBut the simplest fix that addresses the user's concern: **prune BEFORE adding, not after, and be more aggressive (prune enough to get to 28, not just 35)**.","thinkingSignature":"d7ef6ed2af35193d88cce8d07bb1572ef2a61c2e26f35fc6e2c5a323d265f1cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zbpc406out61_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：先清空间，再添加，最后再清一次（保持 ~30）\n# disposability 排序：auto-ingested → 行数少 → 最先删\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\n\nTARGET=30\nBUFFER=5   # 超过 TARGET+BUFFER 才触发 prune\nARCHIVE_MARK=\"__archived__\"  # 防止重复处理\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\n# 分数 = (是否auto-ingested? 0:100) + 行数\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score=0\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=100  # 手动创建的不轻易删\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：执行 prune 到目标数量 =====\nprune_to_target() {\n    local target=$1\n    local current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    local pruned=0\n\n    while [ \"$current\" -gt \"$target\" ]; do\n        # 找可丢弃分数最低的文件（最可丢弃的）\n        local victim=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | while read f; do\n            echo \"$(disposability_score \"$f\") $f\"\n        done | sort -n | head -1 | cut -d' ' -f2-)\n\n        [ -z \"$victim\" ] || [ ! -f \"$victim\" ] && break\n\n        local fname=$(basename \"$victim\")\n        mv \"$victim\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n        echo \"  🗑  精简: $fname\"\n        pruned=$((pruned + 1))\n        current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    done\n\n    [ \"$pruned\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔪 精简完成: 移出 $pruned 个\"\n}\n\n# ===== 1. 先清空位：当前超过 TARGET+BUFFER 就先清理 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt $((TARGET + BUFFER)) ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 前置清理: 当前 $CURRENT 个，先精简到 $TARGET\"\n    prune_to_target \"$TARGET\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 2. Ingest: 扫描 skills/ 创建实体页 =====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    [ -d \"$skill\" ] || continue\n    name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n    [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ] && continue\n\n    cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n    echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n    NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\ndone\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 3. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ \"$FIXED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 4. 后置清理：添加后再次检查，超过 TARGET 就精简 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt $((TARGET + 1)) ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 后置清理: 当前 $CURRENT 个，精简到 $TARGET\"\n    prune_to_target \"$TARGET\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 5. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn-once | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED | docs:$DOCS_COUNT\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | fixed:$FIXED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82492,"output":1554,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102933,"cost":{"input":0.024747599999999998,"output":0.0018648,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02774562}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067665533,"responseId":"062bd75272501d79473051db706fc52c"}}
