{"type":"message","id":"13e01df3","parentId":"24023802","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:09:20.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I see the problem. The script:\n1. Started with 42 entities (not the 32 I thought - the previous manual prune must have restored some)\n2. Before prune: 42 → pruned 12 → 30\n3. Then added 21 new skill entities → 51\n4. After prune: 51 → pruned 21 → 30\n\nBut here's the issue: ALL 21 newly added entities are auto-ingested empty templates. They're all getting added and then immediately pruned because they're the most disposable. This is a waste - why add them just to delete them?\n\nThe real problem is: **when there's no space, don't add then delete. Instead, don't add at all.** Or better: **check if there's room BEFORE adding.**\n\n\nThe smarter approach is to measure available space before creating new entities, and only add up to what fits within the target buffer. This prevents the wasteful add-then-delete cycle by only creating entities when there's actually capacity for them.","thinkingSignature":"64249f26156537bc2871bf96ef3122f34b9da7f2da138682600502b6387aca3b"},{"type":"text","text":"问题很清楚：加进去再删是白做工。应该**先算空间，不够就直接跳过新增**。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3wsdofjzy0c7_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 检查空间，有余量才添加新 entity\n#   2. 添加后超了就清理（先加后清 vs 先清后加，选后者更稳）\n#   3. disposability 分数：auto-ingested > 行数少 > 最先删\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\n\nTARGET=30\nBUFFER=5   # 超过 TARGET+BUFFER 才触发 prune\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\n#   auto-ingested = 0分（最优先删）\n#   非 auto-ingested = 500分（保留）\n#   + 行数（越短越先删）\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=500  # 手动创建的尽量保留\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：清理到目标数量 =====\nprune_to_target() {\n    local target=$1\n    local current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    local pruned=0\n\n    while [ \"$current\" -gt \"$target\" ]; do\n        # 选可丢弃分数最低的\n        local victim=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | while read f; do\n            echo \"$(disposability_score \"$f\") $f\"\n        done | sort -n | head -1 | cut -d' ' -f2-)\n\n        [ -z \"$victim\" ] || [ ! -f \"$victim\" ] && break\n\n        local fname=$(basename \"$victim\")\n        mv \"$victim\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n        echo \"  🗑  精简: $fname\"\n        pruned=$((pruned + 1))\n        current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    done\n\n    [ \"$pruned\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔪 精简完成: 移出 $pruned 个\"\n}\n\n# ===== 1. 检查当前空间 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nAVAILABLE=$((TARGET + BUFFER - CURRENT))\necho \"  📊 当前 $CURRENT / 目标 $TARGET / 可新增 $AVAILABLE\"\n\n# ===== 2. 扫描 skills/，按可用空间添加（有空间才添加）=====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nSKIPPED=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    [ -d \"$skill\" ] || continue\n    name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n    [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ] && continue\n\n    # 空间不足则跳过\n    if [ \"$AVAILABLE\" -le 0 ]; then\n        SKIPPED=$((SKIPPED + 1))\n        continue\n    fi\n\n    cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n    echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n    NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n    AVAILABLE=$((AVAILABLE - 1))\ndone\n\n[ \"$SKIPPED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  ⏭  跳过(空间不足): $SKIPPED 个\"\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 3. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ \"$FIXED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 4. 超标清理 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt $((TARGET + BUFFER)) ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 超标清理: 当前 $CURRENT，精简到 $TARGET\"\n    prune_to_target \"$TARGET\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 5. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | skip:$SKIPPED | fixed:$FIXED\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | skip:$SKIPPED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85026,"output":1669,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105582,"cost":{"input":0.025507799999999997,"output":0.0020028,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028643819999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067723713,"responseId":"062bd78cdde8f03b07fffe450d56cf9a"}}
