{"type":"message","id":"d5ef10fe","parentId":"faa0065c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:09:36.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to restore some of the entities that were just pruned since they were actually valuable. Let me check what's currently in entities vs what we want to keep. Also I should think about the manual claude-code entities that were manually created (not auto-ingested) and should be preserved.Actually, looking at the output - the problem is that I was pruning ALL entities because I was pruning down to 30, and there were only ~30 real ones but the pruning was removing the manually-created ones too (because the auto-ingested check was finding them all).\n\nWait, but the issue is different: ALL 21 newly added ones were auto-ingested empty templates (22 lines each), so they all got scored 0+22=22. Then after adding them, we had 51 and needed to prune down to 30. \n\nSo the pruning removed the lowest-scored entries first, which were the newly added templates at 22 points each, along with some other auto-ingested entries. But this means the manually-created ones like `claude-code-architecture.md` and `claude-code-commands.md` got pruned too—they're scoring lower than I expected, which suggests the auto-ingested flag is being set even on entries that should have been manually created.\n\nActually, I see the issue now. The new entities are created with `status: auto-ingested` when they come from skills/, so they're scoring 0+22=22, but the manually-created ones like `claude-code-commands.md` have `status: active` and are scoring 500+30=530. That's why the new ones are getting removed first. Let me just verify what's actually left in the entities directory.","thinkingSignature":"b50376d0789864ca86a7a2bba9562c130490df281ba3014abb286ce649549934"},{"type":"text","text":"测一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hopwlajyibdm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86733,"output":387,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106007,"cost":{"input":0.0260199,"output":0.00046439999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02761752}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067760675,"responseId":"062bd7b0afb07fd0e953800aa0d0b4d1"}}
