{"type":"message","id":"2f10a631","parentId":"5f57f6d9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:11:54.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `claude-code-40-tools-complete-report` etc. are NOT in skills/ directory now. But they're being created as entity files by the wiki-learn script. How?Oh wait - I think I misread the previous output. Let me re-check. When I ran `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ | grep -iE \"report|overview|tool|command|security|telemetry\"`, it showed `claude-code-commands` and `claude-code-security` etc. But these are the 5 REAL skill directories (claude-code-architecture, commands, security, telemetry, tools). The other report files (40-tools-complete-report, etc.) are NOT in skills/.So why does the script report \"Skipped(空间不足): 17\"? Let me re-count: 26 skills - 5 that already have entities = 21 that would need to be added. \n\nThe script output shows 17 skipped because we only had 5 available slots before hitting the target of 30, so 21-5=16, but it says 17... maybe there's an off-by-one or one was actually added. The real problem is that 21 new entities would get created, pushing us from 30 up to 51, and the prune step would then need to remove 21 to get back down to 30. I think what happened is the script was run multiple times, and each time it pruned back to 30, then when it ran again it would re-scan and try to add more.\n\nLooking back at the first run output, it added 17 new entities starting from 32, so 32+17=49, then pruned down to 44. But then the second run started with 42 instead of 44, which doesn't match. I think the issue is that some of those 17 newly created entity files in the entities directory were created with underscores in their names because the skill directories had underscores, but then later when the entities got their hyphens normalized, there's a mismatch between what was created and what the script is seeing now. I'm tracking the cycle: starting at 41 entities, the script skips adding 17 due to space constraints, then prunes 11 down to 30. But I need to figure out which 11 files were actually removed in that prune step to understand what's happening with the entity count. I'm seeing the core issue now—there's a mismatch between the 26 skills in the directory and the 17 entities being created, which suggests some skills are creating multiple entities or there's a naming collision happening. The fact that the entity count stays at 30 after pruning indicates the same 11 files keep getting removed repeatedly, while the other 6 entities persist because they're manually-created or high-line-count files that don't meet the deletion criteria. So the real problem is that manually-created entities like `ai-usage.md`, `backup-strategy.md`, and `openclaw.md` have high priority scores (500+ lines) and aren't being removed, while the auto-ingested ones are scoring too low (0+28=28) and keep getting pruned. I need to either increase the minimum line threshold for auto-ingested entries to prevent them from being treated as disposable, or manually remove the old underscore-version entities and switch to hyphenated naming to reduce the initial count. So with 21 new entities being added, I'd prune 18 down to exactly 30—but the actual run only removed 11, which means something's off. I'm looking at the pruning output and realizing those first four files (agent-team-orchestration, 40-tools-complete-report, architecture-overview, architecture) are the same ones that appeared in the previous run, suggesting they were restored from archive and are now competing for deletion again.\n\nThe real issue is that my archive and entity directories are filling up with duplicate files of the same entities. I should clear out the skills directory entirely, remove all auto-ingested entities, and start fresh with just the manually-created ones, letting the cron job rebuild everything cleanly.","thinkingSignature":"da54f410b7a404485f7b383b5c60ce752f586398a9bfbd5ce06d49007f58662a"},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了：skills/ 里有 26 个目录（含 underscore 命名的旧 entity 污染），entity 里有41个。脚本每跑一次就往复删加 11 个，永远不稳定。\n\n彻底重置一次：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k8a9wuvd5q2c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 清理：移出所有 auto-ingested 实体 ===\"\nARCHIVE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive\"\nENTITIES=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities\"\nmkdir -p \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\n# 统计\nauto_count=$(grep -l \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nmanual_count=$(grep -l \"status: active\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"当前: auto-ingested=$auto_count, manual=$manual_count, 总计=$(ls $ENTITIES/*.md | wc -l)\"\n\n# 移出所有 auto-ingested\nfor f in \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md; do\n    [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        fname=$(basename \"$f\")\n        mv \"$f\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 清理后 entities/ ===\"\nls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md | wc -l\nls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md | sort"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91096,"output":1149,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111132,"cost":{"input":0.0273288,"output":0.0013788,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02984082}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776067875705,"responseId":"062bd823f61f14f905468dcc6f9ca257"}}
