{"type":"message","id":"e745ff67","parentId":"76db52e6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:56:54.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the picture is clear:- skills/ has 26 real skill directories- entities/ has 16 auto-ingested ones (the ones matching skill directories)- entities/ has 25 manual ones (the ones NOT matching skill directories = ai-usage, backup-strategy, config, corrections, error-handling, framework, ingest, lint, llm-wiki-*, log, memory, openclaw, preferences, query, search, skills, system-integration, task-orchestrator, user, v8-scorer, wiki-evvolution)\n- 25 manual + 16 auto-ingested = 41 total16 of the auto-ingested ones match skill directories. \n\nThe script only ingests from skills/ directories that don't already have corresponding entity files, so when it runs on the 26 skill directories, it skips any that already have entities and only creates new ones for the missing ones. So 16 auto-ingested entities matched their skill directories, leaving 10 skills without entities, which means the script should add those 10 new ones—but it reported adding 17 instead. There's a discrepancy I need to figure out.\n\nThe script scans skills/ every hour and creates entities for directories that don't have matching .md files, but I'm realizing the cron run might have ingested entities that were previously deleted and moved to the archive, then re-ingested them. Also, the script checks the source skills/ directory (like `agent-team-orchestration`) rather than the entity file itself, so the logic might be working differently than I thought. I'm realizing the math works out—16 auto-ingested entities plus 25 manual ones gives 41 total, which matches what I'm seeing. The 10 uningested skills should fill the gap to reach the target of 30, but the report shows 17 new entities were added. I think the issue is that the manual entities were created before those 10 skills existed, so they've always been separate from the ingestion process.\n\nLet me just accept the current state and focus on whether the system is actually stable. I could add a tracking mechanism to distinguish between newly ingested skills and re-ingested ones, or I could raise the target to 45 to better reflect the natural balance between manual and auto-ingested entities. The real question is whether the framework is fundamentally working or if there's still an operational issue causing instability.\n\nLooking at the core problems: the cron delivery error is fixed, but the entities count of 41 keeps cycling through a waste loop. The cleanest fix would be to separate auto-ingested skills from manual entities and target around 25-30 of each, but since skills/ has exactly 26 items, the system naturally wants to stabilize around that number plus manual additions. I should just move the TARGET to 45 and accept that with 26 skills and ~15 manual entities, we'll see some auto-pruning happening.\n\nThe real problem is the re-ingestion cycle where skills get pruned then re-added repeatedly. I could track what's been ingested before and skip re-ingesting deleted items, or I could just accept that the auto-prune will stabilize around 41-42 and accept this as the new steady state. The simplest fix would be to only create entities for new skills that don't already exist as auto-ingested, and let the prune handle the rest.\n\nActually, wait—if I delete an auto-ingested entity and it's still in skills/, the next cron run will just re-create it. So I need to track what's been ingested and deleted to avoid this cycle. Or I could just stop adding auto-ingested entities from skills altogether and only keep manual ones, but that defeats the purpose of the cron. Let me reconsider—the wiki-learn cron is supposed to automatically ingest new skills, so I should only skip entities that have been manually promoted to \"active\" status, not auto-ingested ones.\n\nI think the cleanest approach is to record ingested skills in a hidden file like `.ingested`, then check that file before re-ingesting anything. This breaks the wasteful cycle without requiring manual intervention every time a new skill is added. Let me update the script with this logic.","thinkingSignature":"69f32f8e78f3b1e765747a247b45f666b6593f7b4d4f4cb821919c8896aa931d"},{"type":"text","text":"skills/ 有 26 个真 skill，16 个已经摄入 auto-ingested，10 个未摄入。问题是：被 prune 删掉的，下次 cron 又重新从 skills/ 摄入——形成循环。需要在脚本里记录已删除的，跳过重摄入：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ahs41g23b87q_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96349,"output":927,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116163,"cost":{"input":0.0289047,"output":0.0011124,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03115032}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776070577775,"responseId":"062be2b1b61eda30539994151b55d252"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0a5b40f","parentId":"e745ff67","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:56:54.766Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ahs41g23b87q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 检查空间，有余量才添加新 entity\n#   2. 添加后超了就清理（先加后清 vs 先清后加，选后者更稳）\n#   3. disposability 分数：auto-ingested > 行数少 > 最先删\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\n\nTARGET=30\nBUFFER=5   # 超过 TARGET+BUFFER 才触发 prune\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\n#   auto-ingested = 0分（最优先删）\n#   非 auto-ingested = 500分（保留）\n#   + 行数（越短越先删）\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=500  # 手动创建的尽量保留\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：清理到目标数量 =====\nprune_to_target() {\n    local target=$1\n    local current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    local pruned=0\n\n    while [ \"$current\" -gt \"$target\" ]; do\n        # 选可丢弃分数最低的\n        local victim=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | while read f; do\n            echo \"$(disposability_score \"$f\") $f\"\n        done | sort -n | head -1 | cut -d' ' -f2-)\n\n        [ -z \"$victim\" ] || [ ! -f \"$victim\" ] && break\n\n        local fname=$(basename \"$victim\")\n        mv \"$victim\" \"$ARCHIVE/$fname\"\n        echo \"  🗑  精简: $fname\"\n        pruned=$((pruned + 1))\n        current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    done\n\n    [ \"$pruned\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔪 精简完成: 移出 $pruned 个\"\n}\n\n# ===== 1. 检查当前空间 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nAVAILABLE=$((TARGET + BUFFER - CURRENT))\necho \"  📊 当前 $CURRENT / 目标 $TARGET / 可新增 $AVAILABLE\"\n\n# ===== 2. 扫描 skills/，按可用空间添加（有空间才添加）=====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nSKIPPED=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    [ -d \"$skill\" ] || continue\n    name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n    [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ] && continue\n\n    # 空间不足则跳过\n    if [ \"$AVAILABLE\" -le 0 ]; then\n        SKIPPED=$((SKIPPED + 1))\n        continue\n    fi\n\n    cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n    echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n    NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n    AVAILABLE=$((AVAILABLE - 1))\ndone\n\n[ \"$SKIPPED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  ⏭  跳过(空间不足): $SKIPPED 个\"\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 3. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ \"$FIXED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 4. 超标清理 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt $((TARGET + BUFFER)) ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 超标清理: 当前 $CURRENT，精简到 $TARGET\"\n    prune_to_target \"$TARGET\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 5. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | skip:$SKIPPED | fixed:$FIXED\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | skip:$SKIPPED\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776070614749}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa4b46f0","parentId":"c0a5b40f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:57:46.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the script, the issue is that `prune_to_target` moves files to archive, but when the script runs again, those skills are still in skills/, so they'll be re-ingested. I need to track which skills have been \"soft-deleted\" (pruned) and skip them on future runs.However, the current script already skips entities that exist in entities/ (`[ -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ]`). The problem is the deleted ones DON'T exist in entities/ anymore, so they get re-created.I need a blocklist: a file that tracks pruned skill names that should NOT be re-ingested. \n\nThe cleanest approach is to record pruned skills in a blocklist file and check it before ingesting—if a skill's been pruned before, skip it even if it's no longer in entities/. But I should also think about whether a skill's directory still existing in skills/ means it should be ingested again.\n\nThe real distinction is that `status: active` entities are manually maintained and should stay in the system permanently, while `status: auto-ingested` entities come from skills/ and can be re-ingested if deleted but their source still exists. The solution is to check if a pruned skill's directory is still present before re-ingesting it.\n\nActually, the simplest approach is to only ingest skills that don't already have an entity AND aren't on a blocklist of previously pruned skills. When pruning, I add to this blocklist, and the ingestion phase skips any skill that's been removed before.","thinkingSignature":"613c6514d23aafa674ae1fc3bb69dfe50c18ce48c8e9cd867fad652d19e02f78"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gurtts674bhu_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 只摄入新 skill（不在 entities/ 且不在 blocklist/ 中）\n#   2. blocklist 防止被删的 entity 重复摄入\n#   3. 有空间才添加，超标才 prune\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\nBLOCKLIST=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\"  # 被删除的 skill 名列表\n\nTARGET=30\nBUFFER=5\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n    else\n        score=500\n    fi\n    local lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\")\n    echo $((score + lines))\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：从 blocklist 加载已删除 skill 名 =====\nload_blocklist() {\n    [ -f \"$BLOCKLIST\" ] && cat \"$BLOCKLIST\" || true\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：添加 skill 到 blocklist =====\nblocklist_add() {\n    echo \"$1\" >> \"$BLOCKLIST\"\n}\n\n# ===== 辅助：精简到目标数量（同时写 blocklist）=====\nprune_to_target() {\n    local target=$1\n    local current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    local pruned=0\n\n    while [ \"$current\" -gt \"$target\" ]; do\n        local victim=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | while read f; do\n            echo \"$(disposability_score \"$f\") $f\"\n        done | sort -n | head -1 | cut -d' ' -f2-)\n\n        [ -z \"$victim\" ] || [ ! -f \"$victim\" ] && break\n\n        local fname=$(basename \"$victim\" .md)\n        mv \"$victim\" \"$ARCHIVE/$(basename $victim)\"\n        # 如果 skill 目录还在，加入 blocklist 防止下次重摄入\n        [ -d \"$SKILLS_DIR/$fname\" ] && blocklist_add \"$fname\"\n        echo \"  🗑  精简: $fname\"\n        pruned=$((pruned + 1))\n        current=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    done\n\n    [ \"$pruned\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔪 精简完成: 移出 $pruned 个\"\n}\n\n# ===== 1. 加载 blocklist =====\nBLOCKED=$(load_blocklist | tr '\\n' '|')\necho \"  🚫 blocklist: ${BLOCKED:-无}\"\n\n# ===== 2. 检查空间 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nAVAILABLE=$((TARGET + BUFFER - CURRENT))\necho \"  📊 当前 $CURRENT / 目标 $TARGET / 可新增 $AVAILABLE\"\n\n# ===== 3. 扫描 skills/，按空间添加（排除 blocklist）=====\nNEW_ENTITIES=0\nSKIPPED_SPACE=0\nSKIPPED_BLOCK=0\nfor skill in \"$SKILLS_DIR\"/*/; do\n    [ -d \"$skill\" ] || continue\n    name=$(basename \"$skill\")\n\n    # 已在 entities/ 中则跳过\n    [ -f \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" ] && continue\n\n    # 在 blocklist 中则跳过（曾被删除，不重摄入）\n    if [ -n \"$BLOCKED\" ] && echo \"$BLOCKED\" | grep -qE \"(^|)$name(|)$\"; then\n        SKIPPED_BLOCK=$((SKIPPED_BLOCK + 1))\n        continue\n    fi\n\n    # 空间不足则跳过\n    if [ \"$AVAILABLE\" -le 0 ]; then\n        SKIPPED_SPACE=$((SKIPPED_SPACE + 1))\n        continue\n    fi\n\n    cat > \"$ENTITIES/${name}.md\" << EOF\n---\ntitle: $name\ntype: skill\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\ntags: [skill, auto]\n---\n\n# $name\n\n> 自动从 skills/ 目录摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: skill\n- 路径: skills/$name\n- 摄入时间: $(date \"+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[skills]] - 技能清单\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 使用方式\nEOF\n    echo \"  📥 新技能实体页: $name\"\n    NEW_ENTITIES=$((NEW_ENTITIES + 1))\n    AVAILABLE=$((AVAILABLE - 1))\ndone\n\n[ \"$SKIPPED_BLOCK\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🚫 跳过(blocklist): $SKIPPED_BLOCK 个\"\n[ \"$SKIPPED_SPACE\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  ⏭  跳过(空间不足): $SKIPPED_SPACE 个\"\n\n# 扫描 docs/ 作为 Raw Sources\nDOCS_COUNT=$(ls \"$WORKSPACE/docs\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"  📂 Raw Sources: docs/$DOCS_COUNT\"\n\n# ===== 4. Lint: 死链检查与修复 =====\nFIXED=0\nfor link in $(grep -roh '\\[\\[[a-z0-9-]*\\]\\]' \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/\\[\\[//;s/\\]\\]//g' | sort -u); do\n    if [ ! -f \"$ENTITIES/${link}.md\" ]; then\n        sed -i \"s/\\[\\[$link\\]\\]//g\" \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null\n        FIXED=$((FIXED + 1))\n    fi\ndone\n[ \"$FIXED\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  🔧 修复死链: $FIXED 个\"\n\n# ===== 5. 超标清理 =====\nCURRENT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [ \"$CURRENT\" -gt $((TARGET + BUFFER)) ]; then\n    echo \"  🔪 超标清理: 当前 $CURRENT，精简到 $TARGET\"\n    prune_to_target \"$TARGET\"\nfi\n\n# ===== 6. 记录 log =====\nENTITY_COUNT=$(ls \"$ENTITIES\"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"## [$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] wiki-learn | entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES | skip(block):$SKIPPED_BLOCK | skip(space):$SKIPPED_SPACE | fixed:$FIXED\" >> \"$LOG\"\n\necho \"  ✅ entities:$ENTITY_COUNT | new:$NEW_ENTITIES\"\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 完成 ===\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98686,"output":1979,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119552,"cost":{"input":0.029605799999999998,"output":0.0023748,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033113819999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776070614769,"responseId":"062be2d6ac1b538c15e7b8e2cd96beb2"}}
