{"type":"message","id":"b2cb3a36","parentId":"beee0cf1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:58:20.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The blocklist has duplicate entries now (because it was initialized and then items were added again during pruning). Let me clean up the blocklist - it should only contain the 9 original skill names. Also, the entities are now at 30.\n\nLet me clean up the blocklist so it only has unique entries, and also do the same for the entity-archive. The entity-archive has accumulated a lot of files. Let me leave it for now since it's archive.\n\nAlso, I need to update the MEMORY.md with the current framework status and the entity count.\n\nLet me also verify the framework as a whole is working properly.\n\nSummary of framework status:\n1. ✅ Gateway (pid 97397) - running on port 3001\n\n\n2. ✅ 3103 scorer - running, /api/score works\n3. ✅ 3105 scene-classifier v2 - running, /classify works (numpy bug fixed)\n4. ✅ bootstrap hook - updated to inject session-summary on /new\n5. ✅ session-summary - generates summary on /new\n6. ✅ ephemeral - captures metadata in real-time\n7. ✅ cron jobs - 4 jobs configured (memory-maintain, memory-keeper, Memory Dreaming Promo, wiki-learn)\n8. ✅ wiki-learn cron - delivery fixed, blocklist prevents re-ingestion\n\n, now stable at 30 entities\n9. ⚠️ openclaw-router (pid 434) - still running but marked as half-finished\n\nI should update MEMORY.md with the correct entity count and note that openclaw-router still needs cleanup.","thinkingSignature":"0908f255149dcddc65270793b5996c6139f87ebdde3a9c23c31cb2af47102a9c"},{"type":"text","text":"稳定在 30 个了。清理 blocklist 重复项，然后更新 MEMORY：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ir7tgkekxodm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 去重 blocklist\nsort -u ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist > /tmp/blocklist_tmp && mv /tmp/blocklist_tmp ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\necho \"blocklist 去重后: $(wc -l < ~/.openclaw/