nly capturing what existed when the session began, not the full conversation that's happened since.\n\nThe real problem is that the current session's new messages aren't being captured in ephemeral at all. I need to add an ephemeral capture hook to the gateway so it records user and assistant messages as they happen, not just at session startup.\n\nThere's also the issue of the bootstrap hook only running once at the start, but since the session is still active with ongoing conversation, I should check whether it's capturing everything it should or if there's a timing issue with how the summary gets injected into the new session context.\n\nThe user is asking me to verify the entire framework works end-to-end without breaking anything, so I need to systematically check each component: the ephemeral capture is missing entirely, session-summary only ran at startup, the bootstrap hook might not be injecting summaries correctly, and the wiki-learn cron had a delivery error. I should trace through each piece to see what's actually broken versus what just needs verification.\n\nLet me start by checking if ephemeral capture is even implemented in the message hooks, since that's foundational to the whole system.","thinkingSignature":"9a5cfb7dd9aba11e906962d6c9b822d567b1f7a92653ea529df3c65707a182bf"},{"type":"text","text":"好，系统性跑一遍。先检查每个断点：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9dx1ff5iui44_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 ephemeral 捕获 hook ===\"; cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh 2>/dev/null | head -30; echo; echo \"=== 检查所有 hook ===\"; ls ~/.openclaw/hooks/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":674,"cacheRead":119041,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119769,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0008087999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00714246,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007967459999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776071072993,"responseId":"062be4a56e026c20ae809371a5ab0379"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c3f86f7","parentId":"d9ce7ea1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:05:12.955Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9dx1ff5iui44_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 ephemeral 捕获 hook ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:18790\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 HTTP 服务\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context/add\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true\nfi\n=== 检查所有 hook ===\nHOOK.md\nauto-score-classify\ncontext-hook.js\nhandler.js\nhandler.ts\non-command-error.sh\non-message.sh\nself-improvement.js\nsession-summary"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"=== 检查 ephemeral 捕获 hook ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:18790\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 HTTP 服务\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context/add\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true\nfi\n=== 检查所有 hook ===\nHOOK.md\nauto-score-classify\ncontext-hook.js\nhandler.js\nhandler.ts\non-command-error.sh\non-message.sh\nself-improvement.js\nsession-summary","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776071112941}}
