{"type":"message","id":"90a7af26","parentId":"6bacb251","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:07:22.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No 2026-04-13-09.jsonl file! The ephemeral isn't being written for the current hour. But context.json WAS updated at 17:04 CST (09:04 UTC). The hook runs and updates context.json but doesn't write ephemeral.\n\nLet me look at the `isMeaningful` function again. It requires either:\n1. Explicit user intent patterns\n2. `c.intercepted === true`3. `c.scene === 'fault_recovery'`4. `s.factors?.risk >= 3`\n5. `s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK'`The current scoring result was score=24, risk=0. None of the meaningful patterns match this message \"[Mon 2026-04-13 17:04 GMT+8] 不破坏整体的前提下，对整体框架进行跑通，你自己自动进行\". \n\nSo the message didn't pass the `isMeaningful` filter, which explains why ephemeral wasn't written. That's actually correct behavior—the hook should filter for genuinely important events. The `isMeaningful` check makes sense: it only captures messages that are either explicitly requested by the user, involve system-level issues, carry high risk, or are part of critical infrastructure.\n\nFor testing purposes though, I should write a test entry directly to ephemeral to verify the whole pipeline works end-to-end, and then check whether the session-summary hook would even trigger on the current session. The session-summary hook only fires on command events like `/new` or `/reset`, not on regular conversation, so it wouldn't run during normal chat. I need to verify the bootstrap hook is properly injecting the summary into new sessions instead.\n\nLooking at my handler.js implementation, I read the most recent `*-session-summary.md` file and inject it as a virtual bootstrap file called `PREVIOUS_SESSION_SUMMARY.md` when the agent bootstraps. This approach should work correctly as long as the hook is being called and the file is being found. Let me verify the hook is actually executing by checking if the gateway is calling the handler.\n\njs file, and I should also test the session-summary pipeline to make sure everything is functioning end-to-end.","thinkingSignature":"b5159137a65682d51921c348b04ac2018f76cf768b520a469d80000a7cc89938"},{"type":"text","text":"ephemeral 检查完毕——`isMeaningful` 过滤了当前消息（风险=0，无关键模式），这是对的。现在做端到端验证，写一条测试 ephemeral + 触发 session-summary：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sye0s1wq6mub_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 写一条有意义测试ephemeral\necho '{\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T09:05:00.000Z\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"text\":\"整体框架端到端测试\",\"textPreview\":\"整体框架端到端测试\",\"classification\":{\"scene\":\"task_multi_step\",\"confidence\":0.8,\"intercepted\":false},\"scoring\":{\"score\":65,\"factors\":{\"risk\":3,\"logic\":1,\"duration\":2,\"resource\":0,\"uncertainty\":1,\"dependency\":1},\"recommendedStrategy\":\"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\"timeout\":180}}' >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/2026-04-13-09.jsonl\n\necho \"写入成功，验证:\"\ntail -1 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/2026-04-13-09.jsonl | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107266,"output":701,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126854,"cost":{"input":0.0321798,"output":0.0008412,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03415422}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776071220444,"responseId":"062be5320546ff3592824e1e1540098f"}}
