{"type":"message","id":"83b65408","parentId":"1d82132f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:08:27.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! But entities is back to 41. That means the wiki-learn cron ran and added entities. Let me check what happened.Wait - the cron ran 6 minutes ago and it shows status \"ok\" now (not \"error\" anymore since we fixed delivery to \"none\"). But entities went from 30 to 41. This means the cron re-ingested things that were pruned.Let me check the blocklist to see what happened.","thinkingSignature":"681148c7e3dd9c3842e79591ca163d365371ce6f45e107b35698c6077f58e35f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_84hqhfzaq6si_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== entities 41 详情 ===\"; for f in ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md; do status=$(grep \"^status:\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null | head -1); lines=$(wc -l < \"$f\"); echo \"$lines $status $(basename $f)\"; done | sort -n | tail -20; echo; echo \"=== blocklist ===\"; cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110269,"output":219,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129375,"cost":{"input":0.0330807,"output":0.0002628,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034476719999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776071301515,"responseId":"062be5847428c5143c50a1eb8ec22a7b"}}
