{"type":"message","id":"b2572b66","parentId":"f7d9ecb0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:32:26.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both 3105 and 3103 work fine from the same environment. So the hook's API calls should work too. But context.json shows `classification: null`. \n\nThis means the hook IS running but the API call to 3105 is failing for some reason. Or there's a race condition in the sessionKey resolution.\n\nWait - let me re-read the context.json:\n```json\n{\n    \"classification\": null,\n    \"scoring\": {\n        \"score\": 24,\n        ...\n    },\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-13T09:04:18.772Z\",\n    \"messagePreview\": \"[Mon 2026-04-13 17:04 GMT+8] 不破坏...\"\n}\n```\n\nThe timestamp is 09:04:18 UTC (17:04 GMT+8), which was the first user message. The 17:30 update only changed the scoring portion, not the classification field - so the hook is running for each message but the classification call to 3105 is consistently returning null, even though the curl test works fine from the same environment.\n\nLooking at the update time of 17:30:59 and comparing it to the last curl test around 17:30, they're aligned. This suggests the hook ran after that test and successfully called 3103 for scoring (getting 24), but the classification call to 3105 failed - possibly a timeout or the API request got truncated somehow.\n\nI need to check whether 3105 actually supports POST requests with a `text` field and returns the expected response format, or if the issue is with how the request is being constructed.","thinkingSignature":"3bfe39fe3402d80a9d59c00bffcf355377092a247fc321627efdb95f8df39457"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qh3wuq9qmzcm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3105/classify 完整响应 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"框架检测\"}' 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3105 是否还有其他endpoint ===\"\ncurl -s http://localhost:3105/ 2>/dev/null | head -c 100\ncurl -s http://localhost:3105/health 2>/dev/null | head -c 100\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3105进程状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep 88283 | grep -v grep | awk '{print $1,$2,$3,$4,$11}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32418,"output":507,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51812,"cost":{"input":0.0097254,"output":0.0006083999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.011467020000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776072731201,"responseId":"062beb196326e273f05a5b56e3b1fb64"}}
