{"type":"message","id":"262e300b","parentId":"abbac993","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:36:55.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so ephemeral is writable. But the auto-score-classify hook's isMeaningful filter might be preventing writes for most messages.\n\nLet me now compile my critical findings. Let me be systematic:\n\n**CRITICAL BUGS:**\n\n1. **auto-score-classify: classification 永远是 null**\n   - context.json 的 `classification` 字段在 hook 运行时是 null\n   - 3105 API 本身正常（curl/node 测试均通过）\n   - hook 在 gateway 进程内运行时 fetchJSON 到 3105 失败，但到 3103 成功\n   - 3105 和 3103 都监听在 127.0.0.1，curl 都能通\n   - 可能是 gateway 进程内的 http 请求有特殊限制\n\n2. **on-message.sh: 从不上报任何消息**\n   - context-api 始终为 0 messages\n   - hook 不知道是否被触发\n\n**MINOR ISSUES:**\n\n3. **session目录结构异常**: `agent=main=main` 只有 context.json，没有 message history JSONL\n\n4. **session-summary 链路未真正验证**: bootstrap hook 的摘要注入逻辑存在，但从未真正从 session-summary hook 输出过\n\n5. **openclaw-router 占用 3101 但完全闲置**\n\nI'm suspecting the issue might be a node.js version incompatibility in the ES module hook—`http.request` could be behaving differently than what I'm testing with the node command. But I should wrap up the critical analysis and report back to the user.","thinkingSignature":"5d7aceaed7a4c860371c1df9971238aa84b67d20a0d1cafe2da4dfa22de4d7bf"},{"type":"text","text":"现在做最关键的一项验证——强制触发 hook 写 classification：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_abeojqijpf9r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 直接用node测试hook代码到3105 ===\"\nnode --input-type=module << 'EOF'\nimport http from \"http\";\n\nfunction fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 3000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(url, {\n      method: \"POST\",\n      headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n    }, (res) => {\n      let data = \"\";\n      res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n      res.on(\"end\", () => {\n        console.error(\"3105 res status:\", res.statusCode, \"data len:\", data.length);\n        try { resolve(JSON.parse(data)); }\n        catch (e) { console.error(\"JSON parse error:\", e.message); resolve(null); }\n      });\n    });\n    req.on(\"error\", (e) => { console.error(\"3105 NET error:\", e.message); resolve(null); });\n    req.setTimeout(timeoutMs, () => { console.error(\"3105 TIMEOUT\"); req.destroy(); resolve(null); });\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nconst text = \"犀利、严格的进行评审、检查\";\nconst result = await fetchJSON(\"http://127.0.0.1:3105/classify\", { text }, 3000);\nconsole.log(\"classification result:\", result ? \"OK\" : \"NULL\");\nconsole.log(\"scene:\", result?.scene);\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43014,"output":673,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62574,"cost":{"input":0.0129042,"output":0.0008076,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01484502}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776072994686,"responseId":"062bec213cc29dcddc9b3f0de0d6fd69"}}
