{"type":"message","id":"ae7815aa","parentId":"3045fe28","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:37:33.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway token is redacted. I can't access the gateway API directly.\n\nLet me focus on what I know for certain from the critical review:\n\n1. **context.json has `classification: null`** - This is a real bug. The hook runs (context.json gets updated) but classification is always null while scoring works. 3105 API itself is fine (curl/node test OK).\n\n2. **on-message.sh context-api has 0 messages** - The context-api at 3101 has received 0 messages since the hook was created.\n\n3. **openclaw-router is idle** - pid 434 running context-api.js on 3101 with 0 messages. But this might be by design if the gateway doesn't use it.\n \nThe core issue seems to be that auto-score-classify is calling 3105/classify but getting null responses, while 3103 works fine. Both should be reachable from the gateway process since they're all on 127.0.0.1, but something's preventing 3105 from responding correctly in that context. Let me test whether 3105 is actually being invoked or if the gateway is hitting a different endpoint.\n\nThe most likely culprit is that the hook handler code was updated in the files, but the gateway process itself hasn't reloaded those changes. If the gateway cached the old handler with 3108 instead of 3105, it would still be calling the wrong port. Though it's also possible 3105 is only binding to a specific interface rather than 0.0.0.0, which would prevent the gateway from reaching it depending on where each process is running.","thinkingSignature":"212f2ad5d25b3895189f3b97b5f30e7d3d9c64c2632c61578a7233e448f03851"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bplx9tsy9ucg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3105 绑定地址 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 3105\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3103 绑定地址 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 3103\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3104 绑定地址(gateway内部) ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 3104\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 进程网络namespace检查 ===\"\ncat /proc/88283/ns/net 2>/dev/null | head -1\ncat /proc/97397/ns/net 2>/dev/null | head -1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44520,"output":491,"cacheRead":18887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63898,"cost":{"input":0.013356,"output":0.0005892,"cacheRead":0.0011332199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015078419999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776073038469,"responseId":"062bec4d65496b0014371bd8918c424a"}}
