{"type":"message","id":"94f28ad4","parentId":"0f3e754a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:14:09.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p8aw599hi9e9_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== context-api 状态 ===\n{\"messages\":0,\"chars\":0}\n=== openclaw-router 进程 ===\nai 434 /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node\n\n=== on-message.sh ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:3101\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 Context API（openclaw-router）\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"=== context-api 状态 ===\n{\"messages\":0,\"chars\":0}\n=== openclaw-router 进程 ===\nai 434 /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node\n\n=== on-message.sh ===\n#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:3101\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 Context API（openclaw-router）\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776075248991}}
{"type":"message","id":"b30cf236","parentId":"94f28ad4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:14:15.198Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"context-api is still at 0 messages. The on-message.sh points to 3101 which is the context-api. But it's still showing 0 messages. This means either:1. The gateway doesn't call on-message.sh for webchat messages\n2. The hook isn't registered correctly\n3. The MESSAGE var is empty when called\n\nLet me check if the gateway actually calls on-message.sh for webchat messages. I need to understand what kind of hooks the gateway actually fires for webchat.Let me look at what hooks are actually configured in the gateway and what events they fire on.","thinkingSignature":"0ed2da5a14b080e9a5e548fb12b82e36bc1b1c240609694285912abd37f7645d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_so240xcxeoko_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== gateway hooks 注册情况 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nc = json.load(sys.stdin)\nhooks = c.get('hooks', c.get('gateway',{}).get('hooks','not found'))\nprint(json.dumps(hooks, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\" 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查 gateway 是否有 hooks 配置 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nc = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('All keys:', list(c.keys()))\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41169,"output":272,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60336,"cost":{"input":0.0123507,"output":0.00032639999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013810799999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075249006,"responseId":"062bf4f00fc44b22961e0dc13ee4732a"}}
