{"type":"message","id":"0702e43f","parentId":"f742d27e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:14:47.667Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pzmutg46srkr_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✓ ready  │ 🚀 boot-md       │ Run BOOT.md on gateway startup                                            │ openclaw-  │\n│          │                  │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 📎 bootstrap-    │ Inject additional workspace bootstrap files via glob/path patterns        │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ extra-files      │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 📝 command-      │ Log all command events to a centralized audit file                        │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ logger           │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 💾 session-      │ Save session context to memory when /new or /reset command is issued      │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ memory           │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 🔗 memory-core-  │                                                                           │ plugin:mem │\n│          │ short-term-      │                                                                           │ ory-core   │\n│          │ dreaming-cron    │                                                                           │            │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 🎯 auto-score-   │ 每条消息自动调用 v8_classifier(3104) 和 v8_scorer(3103)，结果写入         │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ classify         │ session 状态文件供 agent 读取                                             │ managed    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 📝 session-      │ session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次      │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ summary          │ bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile             │ managed    │\n│          │                  │ 读取刚结束的 session 内容。                                               │            │\n└──────────┴──────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────┘\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"good-shore","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"│\n◇  Config warnings ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                         │\n│  - plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (memory slot set to  │\n│    \"memory-core\") but config is present                                 │\n│                                                                         │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\nHooks (7/7 ready)\n┌──────────┬──────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────┐\n│ Status   │ Hook             │ Description                                                               │ Source     │\n├──────────┼──────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────┤\n│ ✓ ready  │ 🚀 boot-md       │ Run BOOT.md on gateway startup                                            │ openclaw-  │\n│          │                  │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 📎 bootstrap-    │ Inject additional workspace bootstrap files via glob/path patterns        │ openclaw-  │\n│          │ extra-files      │                                                                           │ bundled    │\n│ ✓ ready  │ 📝 command-      │ Log