{"type":"message","id":"2d1b7fa1","parentId":"f45f5aeb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:15:09.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the key parts of the session-summary hook - specifically when it fires and what it does. Let me check the event type and action filter.","thinkingSignature":"941d9415f1517116f35d65f189d3bf498e70c7a7bad28580d1256e16d51d43e1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ruazr7mf40b9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== session-summary hook 触发条件 ===\"\ngrep -n \"event.type\\|event.action\\|session-end\\|session_end\\|agent.*reset\\|new.*session\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js | head -15\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== session-summary hook 的 HOOK.md ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/HOOK.md 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44834,"output":140,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63869,"cost":{"input":0.013450199999999999,"output":0.000168,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014751899999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075305602,"responseId":"062bf529c409300437ba1523dfc336d0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f380ed0","parentId":"2d1b7fa1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:15:10.058Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ruazr7mf40b9_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== session-summary hook 触发条件 ===\n493:  const isTarget = event.type === \"command\" && (event.action === \"new\" || event.action === \"reset\");\n\n=== session-summary hook 的 HOOK.md ===\n---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n## 主题\n{一句话概括}\n\n## 关键决策\n- {决策1}\n- {决策2}（无则省略）\n\n## 重要发现\n- {发现1}\n- {发现2}（无则省略）\n\n## 待跟进\n- {事项1}\n- {事项2}（无则省略）\n```\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 v8 Router (3102) 调用 LLM 生成摘要，超时 20s。\n\n## Bootstrap 读取\n\nsession 启动时，扫描 `memory/` 下最新摘要文件（按修改时间），读入作为上下文。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":46,"aggregated":"=== session-summary hook 触发条件 ===\n493:  const isTarget = event.type === \"command\" && (event.action === \"new\" || event.action === \"reset\");\n\n=== session-summary hook 的 HOOK.md ===\n---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n## 主题\n{一句话概括}\n\n## 关键决策\n- {决策1}\n- {决策2}（无则省略）\n\n## 重要发现\n- {发现1}\n- {发现2}（无则省略）\n\n## 待跟进\n- {事项1}\n- {事项2}（无则省略）\n```\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 v8 Router (3102) 调用 LLM 生成摘要，超时 20s。\n\n## Bootstrap 读取\n\nsession 启动时，扫描 `memory/` 下最新摘要文件（按修改时间），读入作为上下文。","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776075310048}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9522d65","parentId":"3f380ed0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:15:17.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The session-summary hook fires on `command:new` and `command:reset` events. But looking at the hook code:\n\n```javascript\nconst isTarget = event.type === \"command\" && (event.action === \"new\" || event.action === \"reset\");\n```\n\nSo it fires when a `/new` or `/reset` command is issued. This means the session-summary for the CURRENT session is generated when the NEXT `/new` is issued. This is a bit confusing but actually makes sense: when you type `/new`, the hook generates a summary of the session that just ended.\n\nNow let me check if session-summary has ever run successfully. \n\nThe hook needs to read the previous session's content through the context, so if that context isn't being passed correctly, the hook might be silently failing or not finding the data it needs.","thinkingSignature":"2a4c77a9e3be50ee3a9fafd77873778bb64889c96d00f0deef89dc7a79d30627"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_09zpned0o9hg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 现有 session-summary 文件 ===\"\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/*-summary* 2>/dev/null\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/*-session-summary* 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== bootstrap-extra-files hook ===\"\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw hooks info bootstrap-extra-files 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45383,"output":293,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64571,"cost":{"input":0.0136149,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0151002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075310060,"responseId":"062bf52d15c2194facf4a3bc19f11f6f"}}
