{"type":"message","id":"b3b65648","parentId":"f037f4cc","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:16:16.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the bundled session-memory hook. It's a proper hook that:\n1. Saves session context to memory when /new or /reset is issued\n2. Uses `findPreviousSessionFile` to locate the previous session file\n\nThe issue is that the session file for webchat might not be stored in the same location as regular sessions. Earlier I saw that the webchat session directory `~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/` only has a `context.json` file, no `.jsonl` message history file. This means the session content might not be accessible to the session-summary hook.\n\nNow let me understand the complete flow and what's broken:\n\n1. **auto-score-classify**: ✅ Fixed by gateway restart\n\n\n2. **session-summary**: ❌ Never generates real summaries because the session file path resolution might not work for webchat sessions, and even if it did, the hook would need a proper LLM API key to generate them\n3. **bootstrap hook**: ✅ Working but only has the manually created summary to work with\n4. **context-api**: ❌ Dead code\n\nThe real question is whether the session-summary hook actually fires when I issue /new. Let me check if the session-summary hook has ever successfully run by looking at the session files themselves.\n\nThe session directory only contains context.json but no .jsonl file, which means the gateway stores session data in its database rather than as JSONL files. So the session file path that session-summary expects might not exist for webchat sessions at all. I should verify what the current session key actually is from the runtime info, then test whether /new actually triggers session-summary to run. First, let me fix the context-api issue since it appears to be unused code.","thinkingSignature":"e72e9d04c842d3ff176453de2a5139b03131c867e527a6ee4cc64ce0690eb719"},{"type":"text","text":"现在理解全貌了。context-api 是死代码——`on-message.sh` 和 `context-hook.js` 没注册成 hook，gateway 从不调用它们。\n\n现在只做一件事：**确认 session-summary 是否真的在 /new 时触发**。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6h5qnzs8c5ir_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 当前 session 信息 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/sessions/agent\\:main\\:main/context.json | python3 -m json.tool | head -3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== session-summary hook 的触发条件 ===\"\ngrep -n \"event.type\\|event.action\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js | head -10\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== HOOK.md 里的 events 配置 ===\"\ngrep -A3 \"events:\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/HOOK.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48678,"output":535,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68108,"cost":{"input":0.014603399999999999,"output":0.000642,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0163791}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075361177,"responseId":"062bf561a248dba3df1a7787a21a5d66"}}
