{"type":"message","id":"a18f0d28","parentId":"51db5d88","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:18:14.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The most recent session-summary file is still the manually created one at 17:07. The session-summary hook has never generated a new summary since the /new command didn't trigger it (or it failed silently).\n\nNow I have the full picture. Let me summarize the评审结果:\n\n**P0 - 已修复**:\n- classification null → 重启 gateway 后恢复\n\n**P1 - 确认断点**:1. **session-summary hook 从未真正工作**\n   - 触发条件：`command:new`（用户主动输入 /new）\n   - 对于 webchat，session 存储在数据库，不在 .jsonl 文件\n   - 即使触发，hook 读不到 session 内容（因为没有 .jsonl）   - 所以 /new 后 hook 跑了个寂寞，写了个空摘要或者没写\n   - bootstrap hook 注入手写摘要 → 可用但非真实链路\n\n2. **context-api/on-message.sh 是死代码**\n   - 文件存在但没注册成 hook\n   - gateway 从不调用\n   - 占用 pid 434 的资源\n\n**P2 - 无害但可清理**:\n- openclaw-router (pid 434) → context-api 死代码，端口 3101，空转\n\nLet me now compile the final status report.","thinkingSignature":"68a061799d3ad49a7bf253401ab5a61230a1ab9ee2d582dde7cf5e3d6e49922f"},{"type":"text","text":"**/new 发了，但 session-summary 没有新文件生成。** 确认断点。\n\n---\n\n## 跑通结果汇报\n\n**已修复**\n\n| 问题 | 修复方式 | 状态 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| classification null | 重启 gateway（pid 97397→140547） | ✅ 恢复 |\n\n**确认的断点**\n\n**① session-summary 链路从未真正跑通**\n\n```\nsession-summary hook 触发条件: command:new（用户输入 /new）\nwebchat session 存储: gateway 数据库（无 .jsonl 文件）\nhook 读的: context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile → .jsonl 文件\n结果: hook 跑，但读不到内容，写了个寂寞\nbootstrap 注入的是我手写的摘要，不是真实链路产物\n```\n\n**② context-api 是死代码**\n\n```\non-message.sh + context-hook.js → 没注册成 hook\ngateway 从不调用它们\nopenclaw-router (pid 434) 空转 6 小时，0 条消息\n```\n\n**当前框架状态（跑通后）**\n\n```\n核心服务\n├── Gateway (3001)        ✅ 重启后稳定\n├── 3103 scorer           ✅ 正常\n├── 3105 classifier       ✅ 正常（gateway 重启后恢复）\n└── 3102 (gateway LLM)   ✅ session-summary LLM 调用依赖\n\nHook 链路\n├── auto-score-classify   ✅ 已修复，重启后生效\n├── session-summary       ⚠️ 链路通但数据源不匹配（webchat 无 .jsonl）\n├── bootstrap             ✅ 注入手写摘要可用\n└── context-api          ❌ 死代码，可清理\n\nCron\n├── wiki-learn            ✅ 稳定在 30-35 个\n├── memory-maintain       ✅\n├── memory-keeper        ✅\n└── Memory Dreaming       ✅\n\nEntities\n├── 当前 35 个（25 手动 + 10 新 auto-ingested）\n└── blocklist 9 个\n```\n\n**建议处理**\n\n1. **清理 openclaw-router**：杀掉 pid 434，移除死代码\n2. **session-summary 适配 webchat**：需要让 hook 能读 gateway 数据库或通过 API 获取 session 内容\n3. **验证 bootstrap 注入**：下次 /new 时观察是否注入了今天的手写摘要\n\n要继续处理哪项？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54624,"output":750,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74269,"cost":{"input":0.016387199999999998,"output":0.0009,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0184209}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776075472492,"responseId":"062bf5cfb36a4bf2e21c26db08a41edc"}}
