{"type":"message","id":"fc2987d1","parentId":"93f8d078","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:21:33.570Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_24a5kcj2eay6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 14-session.md 内容 ===\n# Session: 2026-04-13 14:00\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 主题\n框架修复完成 + 两层记忆系统部署验证\n\n## 关键决策\n1. 3104 classifier 修好（numpy序列化 + workspace Apr 13新版），端口统一3104\n2. 3103 scorer 修好（text字段兼容）\n3. openclaw-router 判定半成品，disable systemd service\n4. cron 重新配置：wiki-auto-learn每小时，memory-keeper每天4点，memory-maintain每天3点\n5. 两层记忆系统部署：hook实时捕获 → ephemeral/ + session-summary LLM提炼\n6. self-improving hook 改写：bootstrap时注入MEMORY.md + 最近3个摘要\n7. gateway 重启完成，hook 实时记忆验证通过\n\n## 重要发现\n1. bootstrap 机制从未验证：AGENTS.md里的指令只是写在文件里，系统没有自动执行\n2. 修复方法：改 self-improving hook，往 bootstrapFiles push MEMORY.md + summaries\n3. ephemeral 触发条件：keyword(记住/决定用等) OR intercepted OR fault_recovery OR risk>=3 OR MEGA_TASK\n4. 实时记忆验证通过（\"记住我用的是 webchat\" → ephemeral写入成功）\n\n## 待跟进\n- [ ] session-summary 在 /new 时跑通（ephemeral → entity升格）\n- [ ] bootstrap 注入在下个 session 验证\n\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->\n\n---\n\n## 补充：/new 后操作步骤（已写入 MEMORY.md）\n\n在 MEMORY.md 末尾新增了完整链路说明，包括：\n1. 读取历史文件\n2. 提炼 ephemeral\n3. 验证记忆闭环\n4. 确认框架状态\n\n同时更新了 SOUL.md 启动检查规则，强制首次回复前读取 MEMORY.md。\n\n## 已知未验证项\n- session-summary hook\n- bootstrap 注入\n- ephemeral → entity 升格\n\n=== 无会话内容.md ===\n# Session: 2026-04-13 07:17\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n# Session: 2026-04-13 07:17\n\n## 主题\n(无会话内容)\n\n## 关键决策\n无\n\n## 重要发现\n无\n\n## 待跟进\n见原始对话记录\n\n\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"=== 14-session.md 内容 ===\n# Session: 2026-04-13 14:00\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 主题\n框架修复完成 + 两层记忆系统部署验证\n\n## 关键决策\n1. 3104 classifier 修好（numpy序列化 + workspace Apr 13新版），端口统一3104\n2. 3103 scorer 修好（text字段兼容）\n3. openclaw-router 判定半成品，disable systemd service\n4. cron 重新配置：wiki-auto-learn每小时，memory-keeper每天4点，memory-maintain每天3点\n5. 两层记忆系统部署：hook实时捕获 → ephemeral/ + session-summary LLM提炼\n6. self-improving hook 改写：bootstrap时注入MEMORY.md + 最近3个摘要\n7. gateway 重启完成，hook 实时记忆验证通过\n\n## 重要发现\n1. bootstrap 机制从未验证：AGENTS.md里的指令只是写在文件里，系统没有自动执行\n2. 修复方法：改 self-improving hook，往 bootstrapFiles push MEMORY.md + summaries\n3. ephemeral 触发条件：keyword(记住/决定用等) OR intercepted OR fault_recovery OR risk>=3 OR MEGA_TASK\n4. 实时记忆验证通过（\"记住我用的是 webchat\" → ephemeral写入成功）\n\n## 待跟进\n- [ ] session-summary 在 /new 时跑通（ephemeral → entity升格）\n- [ ] bootstrap 注入在下个 session 验证\n\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->\n\n---\n\n## 补充：/new 后操作步骤（已写入 MEMORY.md）\n\n在 MEMORY.md 末尾新增了完整链路说明，包括：\n1. 读取历史文件\n2. 提炼 ephemeral\n3. 验证记忆闭环\n4. 确认框架状态\n\n同时更新了 SOUL.md 启动检查规则，强制首次回复前读取 MEMORY.md。\n\n## 已知未验证项\n- session-summary hook\n- bootstrap 注入\n- ephemeral → entity 升格\n\n=== 无会话内容.md ===\n# Session: 2026-04-13 07:17\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n# Session: 2026-04-13 07:17\n\n## 主题\n(无会话内容)\n\n## 关键决策\n无\n\n## 重要发现\n无\n\n## 待跟进\n见原始对话记录\n\n\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776075693561}}
{"type":"message","id":"596322ec","parentId":"fc2987d1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:22:03.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Very revealing! `2026-04-13-14-session.md` was written by the session-memory hook (bundled), not the session-summary hook. It contains a detailed summary of the session's decisions, findings, and follow-ups. This means the session-memory hook IS working and IS writing meaningful summaries.\n\nBut the file name format is different - `2026-04-13-14-session.md` vs what the session-summary hook would write (`2026-04-13-session-summary.md`).\n\nWait - looking more carefully:\n- `session-memory` writes: `YYYY-MM-DD-HH-session.md`  \n- `session-summary` writes: `YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary.md`\n\n\n- `2026-04-13-session-summary.md` at 17:07 was actually written by me manually, not by the hook. The `2026-04-13-无会话内容.md` at 15:17 is from an earlier run where the hook found no content to work with.\n\nThe session-memory hook has been writing to `2026-04-13-14-session.md` since 13:46, but that's a different hook from the session-summary hook - one's bundled and one is registered. Looking at the hooks list output, I can see session-summary is there, so I need to check if both are actually firing or if one's overwriting the other.\n\nThe real problem is that session-summary failed silently when it couldn't read session content - it wrote \"无会话内容\" without erroring out. What I actually need to do is look at how session-memory successfully gets content from the gateway database, then apply that same approach to session-summary so it can access the session content through the same mechanism.\n\nBut actually, the most straightforward fix is to modify session-summary to read from the memory files that session-memory already generates, rather than trying to access gateway database content directly. This way session-summary could use those files as input instead of failing when the session file is empty. The bootstrap-extra-files hook injects files into the context through `event.context.bootstrapFiles`, and the handler.js registers this hook to fire on the agent:bootstrap event.\n\nSo the actual flow should be: when /new or /reset is called, session-summary generates a summary file, then when the new session starts, bootstrap-extra-files reads that summary and injects it into the new session's context. Both hooks are registered and should be firing, but the issue is that the summary file itself isn't being created properly because session-summary can't access the session content. The bundled session-memory hook is writing the actual session files to `sessions/` directory, but the custom session-summary hook in `~/.openclaw/hooks/` can't find them—likely because it's looking for `previousSessionEntry.sessionFile` which returns null for webchat sessions. I need to check if the bundled hook's session file path follows a different naming convention or location than what the custom hook expects. The hook checks `event.context?.previousSessionEntry?.sessionFile` for the session file path, but when I tested with `/new` via `sessions_send`, it returned null, which is why it fell back to \"无会话内容\". The bundled session-memory hook uses the same mechanism but somehow still manages to locate and read the session file. The hook execution appears to be asynchronous—the `/new` command returned immediately while the hook ran in the background, which is why I couldn't observe the session file state right after the call. I need to add logging to track what's actually happening, or check if the bundled and custom hooks have different file paths or configurations that would explain why one works and the other doesn't.\n\nLooking at the session keys from the actual files, I can see sessions like `agent:main:main` and `agent:fast_agent:main`, which suggests the bundled hook is finding session files that the custom hook isn't. I should verify whether the session file path in the context actually points to a different location than what the custom hook is trying to access. The custom session-summary hook might be reading from the wrong session file path - `agent:main:main` instead of the actual current session. I need to add diagnostic logging to see what session file path the hook is actually receiving, then potentially redirect it to use the bundled hook's session file location instead. The real issue might be that webchat sessions don't have `.jsonl` files at all, so the hook is just falling back to ephemeral entries. If I make the hook prioritize ephemeral data when session content is empty, it could still generate a meaningful summary without needing to fix the session file path problem. The ephemeral data would give it the context it needs from this session's memory fragments.\n\nI should verify that ephemeral is capturing the current session's entries with the right sessionKey, since that's what session-summary would use to pull them.","thinkingSignature":"adc0cc636bac926b3fce1caa7faf244eeb6732df4f4c305f02b198f6d9e151cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_itjcnti5c99j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== ephemeral 当前内容 ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/2026-04-13-09.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    line=line.strip()\n    if not line: continue\n    try:\n        d=json.loads(line)\n        print(d.get('timestamp','')[:16], '|', d.get('sessionKey',''), '|', d.get('textPreview','')[:50])\n    except: print('BAD:', line[:50])\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== session-summary 读取ephemeral的逻辑 ===\"\ngrep -n \"ephemeral\\|prevSessionId\\|entries\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js | head -15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55414,"output":1171,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75480,"cost":{"input":0.0166242,"output":0.0014052,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0191631}},"stopReason":"t