{"type":"message","id":"650ebda4","parentId":"30bbcbbc","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:22:15.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the key issue. Let me trace through what happens when `/new` fires:\n\n1. session-summary hook runs\n2. It calls `resolveSessionFile(event.context)` to get the session file path\n3. For webchat, `previousSessionEntry.sessionFile` might be null or point to a non-existent file\n4. `extractMessages(sessionFile)` returns \"\" (empty)\n5. It reads ephemeral entries using `prevSessionId` which is the **previous session's sessionKey**\n\nFor the webchat session `agent:main:main`:\n- When `/new` fires, `previousSessionEntry.sessionId` would be the old session's key (e.g., `agent:main:main`)\n\n\n- But the ephemeral entries I wrote earlier use that same key, so they should be found\n- The hook would capture those 2 entries from 2026-04-13-09.jsonl\n\nHowever, my test entries have `sessionKey: \"agent:main:main\"` but the hook filters by `ephemeralEntry.sessionKey === sessionKey` where `sessionKey` is actually the **previous session's ID** from the event context, which should match since both reference the same session.\n\nSo the ephemeral entries SHOULD be found. The real problem is that `extractMessages(sessionFile)` is returning empty because the webchat session has no `.jsonl` file, which is why the summary says \"无会话内容\". I need to find a way to give the hook access to the actual conversation content. The gateway likely stores webchat messages in its database rather than as `.jsonl` files, so I should check if session-memory writes conversation content to its summary files and whether session-summary can read those instead.","thinkingSignature":"232c71fd03e9fa11487377110d32b7a2c48e00ff378b39396b2d17181665e7f6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2wxtggcglhda_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== session-memory 生成摘要的逻辑 ===\"\ngrep -n \"generateSummary\\|generate.*LLM\\|slug\\|entryParts\\|Conversation\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/bundled/session-memory/handler.js 2>/dev/null | head -20\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== session-memory 的 LLM 调用 ===\"\ngrep -n \"LLM\\|llm\\|generate\\|openai\\|anthropic\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/bundled/session-memory/handler.js 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56902,"output":510,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76307,"cost":{"input":0.0170706,"output":0.000612,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0188163}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776075723804,"responseId":"062bf6ca12e310fc9cd1a3ea94dd9557"}}
