{"type":"message","id":"ac371a80","parentId":"aebe8dc3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:48:32.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the problem now! Many of the auto-ingested entities are NOT in the blocklist. For example:- `claude-code-40-tools-complete-report.md` is auto-ingested but NOT in blocklist- `claude-code-architecture-overview.md` is auto-ingested but NOT in blocklist- etc.\n\nThe blocklist only has 13 entries, but 16 auto-ingested entities exist. So 3 auto-ingested entities are NOT in the blocklist.\n\nThis means the blocklist was not updated when these entities were created. Looking at the script:- When `prune_to_target` runs, it adds pruned skills to the blocklist- But `claude-code-40-tools-complete-report` etc. were NEVER pruned (they were in the original entities when we started at 41)\n \nSo the blocklist only captured skills that were actively removed, not the ones that were already there from the beginning. The script only adds a skill to blocklist when it gets deleted, so skills that existed before the blocklist mechanism don't get tracked unless they were explicitly pruned later. The blocklist only tracks skills that were actually removed, so skills that existed before blocklisting was implemented—like those auto-ingested entities from the initial state—weren't captured. Since we cleaned up at 17:00, the auto-ingested entities present now are the ones that got re-added after that cleanup, and they're not in blocklist either.\n\nLooking at what happened: we cleared to 25 entities at 17:00, then the script ran multiple times. After the first run added 10 and pruned 11, we were at 35. But then the second run at 17:02 skipped everything because we were already at target, and the third run at 17:10 added those same 10 entities back since they weren't in the blocklist yet—so we stayed at 35.\n\nThe current count of 41 suggests something else ran between 17:10 and 17:57, possibly an older script iteration that added more entities before being superseded by the newer blocklist-aware version.","thinkingSignature":"cf65110af469e1c7f9ae8d0fc217ff7380ca1face8911681fe90faf995f860bd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wrgmjfg5rc6z_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 cron 最后执行输出 ===\"\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw cron runs b3c6834e-c671-4b21-b6d4-0dc9c86f0e84 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69003,"output":513,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88411,"cost":{"input":0.020700899999999998,"output":0.0006156,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0224502}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077297550,"responseId":"062bfcf0eff3f8ed222b548f4620affd"}}
