{"type":"message","id":"52f6b5a7","parentId":"c47251bf","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:50:21.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. The `blocklist_add` function just appends to the file with `>> \"$BLOCKLIST\"`. Every time a skill is pruned, it's added again. If the same skill is pruned multiple times, it gets duplicated entries.\n\nThe fix: in `blocklist_add`, check if the skill is already in the blocklist before adding.\n\nLet me fix this.","thinkingSignature":"1cef4d409b0ce4650a273d57f828bf2244a48452762263ff9671bf15c0055204"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9k8dge9fwyr5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"# ===== 辅助：添加 skill 到 blocklist =====\nblocklist_add() {\n    echo \"$1\" >> \"$BLOCKLIST\"\n}","newText":"# ===== 辅助：添加 skill 到 blocklist（防重复）=====\nblocklist_add() {\n    local name=$1\n    # 跳过已存在的\n    grep -qFx \"$name\" \"$BLOCKLIST\" 2>/dev/null && return\n    echo \"$name\" >> \"$BLOCKLIST\"\n}"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74797,"output":242,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93934,"cost":{"input":0.0224391,"output":0.0002904,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0238632}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077417814,"responseId":"062bfd68c0550294f518377b9961908c"}}
