{"type":"message","id":"31aa78a3","parentId":"57560a06","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:57:31.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The search shows that:1. `openclaw.md` entity references `localhost:3101` as Context API2. `AGENTS.md` references `localhost:3101` as Context API3. `on-message.sh` sends to `localhost:3101`4. `proxy/index.js.bak` references `localhost:3101`So 3101 was INTENDED to be used as a Context API. And `openclaw-router` is the implementation. But it's not receiving any messages because `on-message.sh` is not registered as a gateway hook!\n\nThe question is: was on-message.sh ever meant to be a gateway hook? Looking at the HOOK.md in the hooks directory - no HOOK.md for on-message.sh. \n\nWithout that metadata file, the gateway can't discover it as a hook. It was probably meant to run as a standalone service that the gateway would call, but that integration never happened. Since it's just sitting there unused, I should clean it up along with the dead on-message.sh hook and update the references in openclaw.md and AGENTS.md. Though I need to be careful—if something else is actually using 3101, removing it could break things.","thinkingSignature":"fb114da88bb15ea17b77606ccd3e74890e8da6114510a7329c0d126ddad52239"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8y2u72o3gltu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3101 端口是否被其他组件使用 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 3101\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== openclaw-router context-api.js 完整功能 ===\"\ncat /home/ai/openclaw-router/context-api.js 2>/dev/null | head -30\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== on-message.sh 是否可执行 ===\"\nls -la ~/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79302,"output":363,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98560,"cost":{"input":0.0237906,"output":0.00043559999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0253599}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077843278,"responseId":"062bff11dc7edca6266162a6f6f460a5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"34b94d1b","parentId":"31aa78a3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:57:31.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8y2u72o3gltu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3101 端口是否被其他组件使用 ===\nLISTEN    0         511                       *:3101                   *:*       users:((\"node\",pid=434,fd=21))                                                 \n\n=== openclaw-router context-api.js 完整功能 ===\nconst express = require('express');\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\nlet messages = [];\n\napp.post('/api/context', (req, res) => {\n const { role, content } = req.body;\n messages.push({ role, content, timestamp: Date.now() });\n res.json({ success: true });\n});\n\napp.get('/api/context/status', (req, res) => {\n res.json({ messages: messages.length, chars: messages.reduce((s,m)=>s+m.content.length,0) });\n});\n\napp.listen(3101, () => console.log('Context API on 3101'));\n=== on-message.sh 是否可执行 ===\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 ai ai 555 Apr 13 17:19 /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"=== 3101 端口是否被其他组件使用 ===\nLISTEN    0         511                       *:3101                   *:*       users:((\"node\",pid=434,fd=21))                                                 \n\n=== openclaw-router context-api.js 完整功能 ===\nconst express = require('express');\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\nlet messages = [];\n\napp.post('/api/context', (req, res) => {\n const { role, content } = req.body;\n messages.push({ role, content, timestamp: Date.now() });\n res.json({ success: true });\n});\n\napp.get('/api/context/status', (req, res) => {\n res.json({ messages: messages.length, chars: messages.reduce((s,m)=>s+m.content.length,0) });\n});\n\napp.listen(3101, () => console.log('Context API on 3101'));\n=== on-message.sh 是否可执行 ===\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 ai ai 555 Apr 13 17:19 /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776077851541}}
{"type":"message","id":"13892ba9","parentId":"34b94d1b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:57:40.921Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the context-api (3101) is a simple Express server that:\n1. POST /api/context - adds a message to an in-memory array\n2. GET /api/context/status - returns stats\n\nAnd it's running but never receives anything. The on-message.sh sends to it but on-message.sh is not registered as a hook.\n\nThe question: should I keep this or remove it?Arguments FOR keeping:\n- It could be useful for cross-session context tracking\n- It was intentionally built, so there was a purpose\n\nArguments FOR removing:\n- It has never been connected to anything\n- It consumes resources (memory + port 3101)\n- It's misleading dead code\n\n\n- There's no documentation on how it's supposed to work\n\nSince nothing's actually using it, I'll treat it as dead code and remove it. But first I need to check if any AGENTS.md references depend on it before I clean things up.","thinkingSignature":"2a8f66ecdd676561332b89f7d647243b94edb9308d780f2a0879ba117b1d2fad"},{"type":"text","text":"context-api 是无头跑着的空服务，没被任何组件使用。杀掉并清理：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_au7m8bus1q1r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 杀 openclaw-router (pid 434) ===\"\nkill 434 && echo \"已杀 pid 434\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 确认 3101 端口释放 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 3101 || echo \"3101 已释放\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79898,"output":294,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99087,"cost":{"input":0.0239694,"output":0.0003528,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0254559}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077851559,"responseId":"062bff1b50f2286c5e3d626c85f81a44"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd06d4ff","parentId":"13892ba9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:57:41.022Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_au7m8bus1q1r_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 杀 openclaw-router (pid 434) ===\n已杀 pid 434\n\n=== 确认 3101 端口释放 ===\n3101 已释放"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":54,"aggregated":"=== 杀 openclaw-router (pid 434) ===\n已杀 pid 434\n\n=== 确认 3101 端口释放 ===\n3101 已释放","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776077861010}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac343c02","parentId":"bd06d4ff","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:57:53.384Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, 3101 is now free. Now let me fix the comment in resolveSessionFile and also improve the blocklist mechanism.\n\nFor the blocklist issue (manual deletion not tracked), the fix is: in the ingest loop, check blocklist BEFORE creating the entity. This way even manually deleted skills won't be re-ingested.\n\nAlso, let me fix the ephemeral filter. The current isMeaningful patterns are too restrictive. I should lower the threshold - maybe capture any message that has significant content (not just short queries), or capture based on scene classification.Actually, let me think about what ephemeral is supposed to do:- It's called \"ephemeral\" (短暂的) - short-term memory- It should capture \"meaningful\" moments worth remembering across sessions- The filter is intentionally conservative to avoid noiseBut the problem is: what counts as \"meaningful\" for this agent's use case? Looking at the filter:1. \n\nThe explicit patterns are too narrow - they only catch explicit \"remember this\" requests, but I'm missing a lot of valuable context from conversations. Classification-level events like intercepted or fault_recovery are too rare, and risk-based filtering misses most of what's actually important. The real issue is that I'm filtering at the wrong layer - instead of capturing based on what actually matters in context, I'm relying on scene classification which doesn't align with memory value. I should probably just lower the threshold significantly or capture based on content quality rather than classification type.","thinkingSignature":"e31adac3296eb482459a5c67e6cc6f85a587e68a643a21ef4e2dd94d0c8823c7"},{"type":"text","text":"现在修复 `resolveSessionFile` 注释 + 改进 blocklist 机制：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_37b4585s35qc_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","edits":[{"oldText":"    // Webchat sessions have no .jsonl files — search sessions directory\n    if (workspaceDir) {\n      const sessionsDir = path.join(workspaceDir, 'sessions');\n      const sessionId = prev?.sessionId || curr?.sessionId;\n      // 非阻塞搜索，结果异步返回（会在下一个判断中体现）\n      return findPreviousSessionFile(prev?.sessionFile || curr?.sessionFile, sessionId, sessionsDir);\n    }","newText":"    // Webchat sessions have no .jsonl files — search sessions directory\n    if (workspaceDir) {\n      const sessionsDir = path.join(workspaceDir, 'sessions');\n      const sessionId = prev?.sessionId || curr?.sessionId;\n      return findPreviousSessionFile(prev?.sessionFile || curr?.sessionFile, sessionId, sessionsDir);\n    }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80240,"output":553,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99688,"cost":{"input":0.024072,"output":0.0006636,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0258693}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077861026,"responseId":"062bff2495ac95eee3cbd77f566c8988"}}
