{"type":"message","id":"cdf832e2","parentId":"95b94f5b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:58:21.717Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_afjlt053jawa_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 当前 ephemeral 过滤规则 ===\n}\n\n// ─── Meaningfulness filter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS = [\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n  \n  // 1. Explicit user intent\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n  \n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n  \n  // 3. High risk (>=3)\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  \n  // 4. MEGA task"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":53,"aggregated":"=== 当前 ephemeral 过滤规则 ===\n}\n\n// ─── Meaningfulness filter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS = [\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n  \n  // 1. Explicit user intent\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n  \n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n  \n  // 3. High risk (>=3)\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  \n  // 4. MEGA task","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776077901707}}
{"type":"message","id":"07ec5491","parentId":"cdf832e2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:58:35.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ephemeral filter is too restrictive. Currently it only captures:\n1. Messages with explicit memory intent (\"记住\", \"以后都\", etc.)\n2. Intercepted messages\n3. Fault recovery scenes\n4. High risk (>=3)5. MEGA tasks\n\nThe problem is that most useful conversations don't match any of these. The fix should be to also capture messages that have meaningful content (not just short queries) OR are from certain important scenes.\n\nActually, looking at the classification returned by 3105:- scene: clarify, task, task_status_query, fault_recovery, etc.- confidence: float\n\nI could add: \"if scene is one of [task, task_status_query, fault_recovery, design, code, debug] AND confidence > 0.6\" → meaningfulAlso: \"if text length > 100 chars (substantial content)\" → meaningfulLet me update the isMeaningful function.","thinkingSignature":"30257fd110eab2a24286574e24e33649ab11e96eb7e179b46c0f9da4694b31d8"},{"type":"text","text":"改 ephemeral 过滤规则，降低门槛：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n9hsoonuzi2h_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js","edits":[{"oldText":"function isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n  \n  // 1. Explicit user intent\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n  \n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n  \n  // 3. High risk (>=3)\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  \n  // 4. MEGA task\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n  \n  return false;\n}","newText":"function isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n\n  // 1. Explicit user intent (highest priority)\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n\n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n\n  // 3. High risk or MEGA task\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n\n  // 4. Substantial content (非只言片语)\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n\n  // 5. Medium complexity multi-step tasks\n  if ((s.factors?.logic || 0) >= 2 || (s.factors?.duration || 0) >= 2) return true;\n\n  return false;\n}"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82670,"output":673,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102238,"cost":{"input":0.024801,"output":0.0008076,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0267423}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776077901722,"responseId":"062bff4c2bed5c2d2884e61bdfae13c6"}}
