{"type":"message","id":"fc49a4d8","parentId":"b3fceebc","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:27:07.420Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mumk5phxk1yu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== isMeaningful 当前规则 ===\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n\n  // 1. Explicit user intent (highest priority)\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n\n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n\n  // 3. High risk or MEGA task\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n\n  // 4. Substantial content (非只言片语)\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n\n  return false;"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":52,"aggregated":"=== isMeaningful 当前规则 ===\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n\n  // 1. Explicit user intent (highest priority)\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n\n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n\n  // 3. High risk or MEGA task\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n\n  // 4. Substantial content (非只言片语)\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n\n  return false;","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776079627407}}
{"type":"message","id":"393f3a54","parentId":"fc49a4d8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:27:13.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The change is correct. Now ephemeral will only capture:1. Explicit user intent (remember/decide patterns)\n2. System-level important (intercepted or fault_recovery)3. High risk (risk>=3) or MEGA task\n4. Substantial content (>80 chars)This is a much tighter filter that preserves the \"memory fragments\" design intent.\n\nThe user might also want to restart gateway to pick up the change. Let me ask or just do it.Actually, gateway will pick up the hook on next message since hooks are loaded dynamically. But for immediate effect, a restart is better. However the user hasn't asked for that. Let me just confirm the fix is in place.","thinkingSignature":"d78f535825e6bc144d18db52f9fe664e17f3a1bcca5caac9eae856d386244472"},{"type":"text","text":"已回退。当前规则：\n\n```\nisMeaningful → true 当且仅当：\n1. 显式记忆/决策指令（记住/决定用/别用/改用）\n2. 拦截或故障恢复场景\n3. 高风险（risk≥3）或 MEGA 任务\n4. 内容超过 80 字符\n```\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 完成。gateway 下次消息自动重载 hook，无需重启。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88959,"output":236,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108090,"cost":{"input":0.026687699999999998,"output":0.0002832,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0281046}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776079627423,"responseId":"062c060913fd31137a6337a0fd22b7d5"}}
