{"type":"message","id":"8ca58ea2","parentId":"fc13bbb9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:20.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue clearly:\n\n1. `workspace/skills/v8_classifier` and `skills/v8_classifier` are **different versions**. The workspace one is version 1.1.0 with `top_candidates` format. The actual 3105 service (which I tested) returns `response` field, not `top_candidates`. This means the workspace v8_classifier SKILL.md is outdated.\n\n2. Both v8_scorer directories have identical SKILL.md files.\n\n3. `workspace/skills/v8_classifier` SKILL.md describes the OLD format with `top_candidates`, but the actual 3105 service returns `response` field. This is a documentation mismatch.\n\n\n4. I need to update the v8_classifier SKILL.md to reflect the actual 3105 API response format.","thinkingSignature":"a65f171f03d83471c1869c984394d45cc14cc19facf25e60ccc84fbb9cd7f111"},{"type":"text","text":"发现严重问题：`workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md` 和实际 3105 API **格式不匹配**。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fhxqebgooop0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3105 实际返回格式 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"测试\"}' | python3 -m json.tool\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== workspace v8_classifier SKILL.md 声称的格式 ===\"\ngrep -A5 \"top_candidates\\|response\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98289,"output":324,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117508,"cost":{"input":0.029486699999999998,"output":0.00038879999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0310092}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080589982,"responseId":"062c09ce91093cc26176c6addb3271ec"}}
{"type":"message","id":"22f454f9","parentId":"8ca58ea2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:21.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fhxqebgooop0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3105 实际返回格式 ===\n{\n    \"response\": \"[LLM\\u54cd\\u5e94] \\u57fa\\u4e8e\\u4f60\\u7684\\u8f93\\u5165\\uff0c\\u5efa\\u8bae\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u5982\\u4e0b\\uff1a...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.6213997602462769\n}\n\n=== workspace v8_classifier SKILL.md 声称的格式 ===\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n--\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n--\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":122,"aggregated":"=== 3105 实际返回格式 ===\n{\n    \"response\": \"[LLM\\u54cd\\u5e94] \\u57fa\\u4e8e\\u4f60\\u7684\\u8f93\\u5165\\uff0c\\u5efa\\u8bae\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u5982\\u4e0b\\uff1a...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.6213997602462769\n}\n\n=== workspace v8_classifier SKILL.md 声称的格式 ===\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n--\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n--\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080601122}}
{"type":"message","id":"912b509d","parentId":"22f454f9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:31.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The actual 3105 returns:\n- `response` (string)\n- `scene` (string)\n- `confidence` (float)\n- `intercepted` (boolean)\n- `meta` (string)\n\nBut the workspace v8_classifier SKILL.md describes:\n- `top_candidates` (array) - doesn't exist in actual response\n- `response` - doesn't exist in actual response (the actual field is `[LLM响应]...` which is the actual text)\n- `confidence` (float)\n\nWait, actually the 3105 DOES return `response` as a field. The `response` field contains \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\" which is a text response. \n\nSo there's a real mismatch here: the SKILL.md documents `top_candidates` as the primary classification output, but the actual API returns `scene`, `confidence`, and `meta` as the main classification result. The `response` field exists but contains LLM-generated text rather than the structured classification data. I need to figure out whether the SKILL.md was written for a different version of the API or if `top_candidates` was removed at some point.","thinkingSignature":"38298625a1079eea2ba9c3d46e27e3d675fb05e1a5da1bace7b7b5392d7711a6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m7twsjcan3k2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== skills/v8_classifier SKILL.md（顶层）=== head -40 ===\"\nhead -40 ~/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98892,"output":304,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118091,"cost":{"input":0.0296676,"output":0.0003648,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0311661}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080601137,"responseId":"062c09d80d5100902b11c366c4ea44fb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"07c44090","parentId":"912b509d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:31.116Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m7twsjcan3k2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== skills/v8_classifier SKILL.md（顶层）=== head -40 ===\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.3.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于高性能多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2`（sentence-transformers，768维，多语言支持，较 MiniLM 更强）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离），按 label 去重后取最高权重\n- 训练数据：`synthetic_training_data.py`（55条样本，9类）\n- 模型文件：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/models/scene_classifier.pkl`\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"=== skills/v8_classifier SKILL.md（顶层）=== head -40 ===\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.3.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于高性能多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2`（sentence-transformers，768维，多语言支持，较 MiniLM 更强）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离），按 label 去重后取最高权重\n- 训练数据：`synthetic_training_data.py`（55条样本，9类）\n- 模型文件：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/models/scene_classifier.pkl`\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080611107}}
