{"type":"message","id":"34865482","parentId":"967c15ca","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:37.906Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6y87k9ewh395_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3105 实际是什么服务 ===\nai 88283 0.2 /usr/bin/python3\n\n=== 3105 进程启动命令 ===\n/usr/bin/python3 api_server.py \n=== 3105 源码位置 ===\n0\n1\n10\n11\n12\n/usr/bin/python3.8"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"=== 3105 实际是什么服务 ===\nai 88283 0.2 /usr/bin/python3\n\n=== 3105 进程启动命令 ===\n/usr/bin/python3 api_server.py \n=== 3105 源码位置 ===\n0\n1\n10\n11\n12\n/usr/bin/python3.8","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080617894}}
{"type":"message","id":"a28f7d0c","parentId":"34865482","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:43.477Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3105 is a Python API server. The SKILL.md for v8_classifier describes a KNN-based embedding classifier, but the actual 3105 service seems to use an LLM-based approach (since the response has `[LLM响应]` in it).Let me check what the actual api_server.py does and what the actual classifier format is.","thinkingSignature":"b54f8b0a6a165c4ca50baa7e0e75dfc67f4b30ac0ae9a8854a5c46631c4f3dbb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d787l6lrdgoi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3105 api_server.py 位置 ===\"\nls -la /proc/88283/cwd 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== api_server.py 内容摘要 ===\"\ncat /proc/88283/cwd/api_server.py 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100043,"output":157,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119095,"cost":{"input":0.0300129,"output":0.0001884,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031334999999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080617910,"responseId":"062c09e9eb55bd24236fef9aa82fdac7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddd39267","parentId":"a28f7d0c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:43.567Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d787l6lrdgoi_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3105 api_server.py 位置 ===\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 0 Apr 13 19:43 /proc/88283/cwd -> /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\n\n=== api_server.py 内容摘要 ===\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nScene Classifier API 服务\n启动: python api_server.py\n访问: http://localhost:8080\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nos.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\nfrom fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware\nimport uvicorn\nimport time\n\n# 配置目录\nCONFIG_DIR = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), 'config')\nRULES_FILE = os.path.join(CONFIG_DIR, 'rule_overrides.json')\n\n# 添加路径\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier')\n\nfrom pipeline.orchestrator import PipelineOrchestrator\nfrom feedback.collector import FeedbackCollector\nfrom classifier.rule_classifier import RuleClassifier\n\napp = FastAPI(title=\"Scene Classifier API\", version=\"2.0\")\n\n# CORS 支持\napp.add_middleware(\n    CORSMiddleware,\n    allow_origins=[\"*\"],\n    allow_credentials=True,\n    allow_methods=[\"*\"],\n    allow_headers=[\"*\"],\n)\n\n# 初始化\ntry:\n    pipeline = PipelineOrchestrator()\n    feedback = FeedbackCollector()\n    rule_classifier = RuleClassifier()\n    print(\"Pipeline initialized\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    pipeline = None\n    rule_classifier = RuleClassifier()\n    print(f\"Pipeline init failed: {e}, using rule-based fallback\")\n\n# 熔断器状态\ncircuit_breaker = {\n    \"failures\": 0,\n    \"last_failure\": 0,\n    \"is_open\": False,\n    \"threshold\": 3,  # 连续失败次数\n    \"timeout\": 30,   # 30秒后尝试恢复\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"=== 3105 api_server.py 位置 ===\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai 0 Apr 13 19:43 /proc/88283/cwd -> /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\n\n=== api_server.py 内容摘要 ===\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nScene Classifier API 服务\n启动: python api_server.py\n访问: http://localhost:8080\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nos.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\nfrom fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware\nimport uvicorn\nimport time\n\n# 配置目录\nCONFIG_DIR = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), 'config')\nRULES_FILE = os.path.join(CONFIG_DIR, 'rule_overrides.json')\n\n# 添加路径\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier')\n\nfrom pipeline.orchestrator import PipelineOrchestrator\nfrom feedback.collector import FeedbackCollector\nfrom classifier.rule_classifier import RuleClassifier\n\napp = FastAPI(title=\"Scene Classifier API\", version=\"2.0\")\n\n# CORS 支持\napp.add_middleware(\n    CORSMiddleware,\n    allow_origins=[\"*\"],\n    allow_credentials=True,\n    allow_methods=[\"*\"],\n    allow_headers=[\"*\"],\n)\n\n# 初始化\ntry:\n    pipeline = PipelineOrchestrator()\n    feedback = FeedbackCollector()\n    rule_classifier = RuleClassifier()\n    print(\"Pipeline initialized\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    pipeline = None\n    rule_classifier = RuleClassifier()\n    print(f\"Pipeline init failed: {e}, using rule-based fallback\")\n\n# 熔断器状态\ncircuit_breaker = {\n    \"failures\": 0,\n    \"last_failure\": 0,\n    \"is_open\": False,\n    \"threshold\": 3,  # 连续失败次数\n    \"timeout\": 30,   # 30秒后尝试恢复\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080623558}}
{"type":"message","id":"66932f3b","parentId":"ddd39267","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:55.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\n1. 3105 is the Scene Classifier API v2.0, which uses a PipelineOrchestrator (ML-based) with a rule-based fallback.\n2. The SKILL.md at `workspace/skills/v8_classifier/` describes an OLD version of the classifier with `top_candidates` format.\n3. The actual response format is `{response, scene, confidence, intercepted, meta}`.\n\nBut wait - let me look more carefully. The actual API returns `response` which is \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\". This is NOT the scene classification result. The scene classification seems to be in the `scene`, `confidence`, and `meta` fields. \n\nSo the `response` field is just the LLM's text response, while `scene` is the actual classification label. But the SKILL.md documentation shows a completely different format with `top_candidates` as the main field, which means the documentation is outdated and doesn't match what's actually being returned.\n\nThe real issue is that when `auto-score-classify` calls 3105, it gets back `{response, scene, confidence, intercepted, meta}` but the hook only uses `classification.scene` and `classification.intercepted`, completely ignoring the `response` field. This suggests the classifier was redesigned at some point to include LLM-generated responses alongside the classification results, but the hook never got updated to handle this new structure. The skill description and actual API behavior are misaligned—the skill claims to route based on `top_candidates`, but the real 3105 API returns a different structure. Since the auto-score-classify hook only reads `scene` and `intercepted` from what the classifier returns, the skill documentation is technically inaccurate even if the routing logic works correctly.","thinkingSignature":"35047cabf3a59657c8e32f9bf0af98619aca980e4955c1aca5cb9796a89e7ef6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6o8qf2ohxdt5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 auto-score-classify 实际用到了什么字段 ===\"\ngrep -n \"classification\\.\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100641,"output":433,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119969,"cost":{"input":0.0301923,"output":0.0005195999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031845599999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080623571,"responseId":"062c09eede42dca151a72c95815d7425"}}
