{"type":"message","id":"48076495","parentId":"1ada21ed","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:43:58.688Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3l2krnqsjzw5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== isMeaningful 中 classification 字段使用 ===\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n\n  // 1. Explicit user intent (highest priority)\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n\n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n\n  // 3. High risk or MEGA task\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n\n  // 4. Substantial content (非只言片语)\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n\n  return false;"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":46,"aggregated":"=== isMeaningful 中 classification 字段使用 ===\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n\n  // 1. Explicit user intent (highest priority)\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n\n  // 2. System-level important\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n\n  // 3. High risk or MEGA task\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n\n  // 4. Substantial content (非只言片语)\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n\n  return false;","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080638677}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4f79a82","parentId":"48076495","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:09.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the auto-score-classify hook uses:- `classification.intercepted`\n- `classification.scene`\n- `scoring.factors.risk`\n- `scoring.recommendedStrategy`\n\nThe actual 3105 response:\n- `scene` ✓ used\n- `intercepted` ✓ used\n- `confidence` - not used (but maybe should be?)\n- `response` - not used\n- `meta` - not used\n\nThe SKILL.md for workspace/v8_classifier talks about `top_candidates` which doesn't exist in the actual response. The actual 3105 response has:\n- `scene` (string) - what the SKILL.md calls the \"primary label\"\n\n\n- `confidence` (float) - similarity score (0-1)\n- `meta` (string) - additional metadata\n- `intercepted` (boolean) - whether it was hard-blocked\n\nThe workspace SKILL.md is documenting the wrong API format entirely, while the actual 3105 service has already evolved past what the documentation describes. The hook is only using a subset of the available fields, so I need to figure out what the SKILL.md should actually be documenting.\n\nThe priority should be fixing the SKILL.md to match the real API, then deciding whether the hook needs to handle more fields like `confidence` and `meta`. I should also check what the context.json does with the classification data. But I'm noticing something odd - the 3105 response shows `[LLM响应]` which suggests an LLM is involved, yet the 3105 process is running Python with `paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2`. Looking at the response format more carefully, there's a disconnect between what the embedding/KNN pipeline should return and what's actually coming back.\n\nThe `[LLM响应]` in the `response` field doesn't match a KNN classifier's typical output, which makes me wonder if the pipeline got replaced with an LLM call at some point, or if the 3105 service has been reimplemented entirely.","thinkingSignature":"b392f4d45d50d5d92c6308473e25e230ec41f062b66691be546afa6542ff9218"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a9a774r7b90s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3105 pipeline orchestrator ===\"\ncat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/pipeline/orchestrator.py 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101400,"output":478,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120773,"cost":{"input":0.03042,"output":0.0005736,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0321273}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080638693,"responseId":"062c09fc8e9d1ec286377085051bd315"}}
{"type":"message","id":"045241df","parentId":"c4f79a82","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:10.032Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a9a774r7b90s_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 3105 pipeline orchestrator ===\n\"\"\"\n主流水线：整合硬拦截、分类（含元判断）、模板注入、LLM调用、后置校验、日志记录\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport time\nimport uuid\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 导入各模块\nfrom interceptors.critical_interceptor import critical_intercept\nfrom templates.template_map import TEMPLATE_MAP\n\n# 尝试加载模型分类器，失败则用规则分类器\nSCENE_CLASSIFIER_DIR = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\nMODEL_PATH = os.path.join(SCENE_CLASSIFIER_DIR, \"models/scene_classifier.pkl\")\n\ntry:\n    os.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n    from classifier.scene_classifier import SceneClassifier\n    classifier = SceneClassifier.load(MODEL_PATH)\n    print(f\"Loaded embedding classifier from {MODEL_PATH}\")\nexcept (ImportError, FileNotFoundError) as e:\n    print(f\"Using rule-based fallback classifier: {e}\")\n    from classifier.rule_classifier import RuleClassifier\n    classifier = RuleClassifier()\n\n\nclass PipelineOrchestrator:\n    def __init__(self, log_file=None):\n        if log_file is None:\n            # 使用绝对路径\n            base_dir = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\n            log_file = os.path.join(base_dir, \"logs/meta_events.jsonl\")\n        self.log_file = log_file\n        self.llm_call = self._mock_llm  # 可替换为真实LLM调用\n        \n        # 确保日志目录存在\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(log_file) if os.path.dirname(log_file) else \"logs\", exist_ok=True)\n    \n    def process(self, user_input, context=None):\n        \"\"\"\n        处理单次用户输入\n        context: dict，可包含 task_id, history 等\n        \"\"\"\n        meta_events = []\n        response = None\n        \n        # 1. 硬拦截\n        block = critical_intercept(user_input)\n        if block:\n            meta_events.append({\"stage\": \"critical_intercept\", \"action\": \"blocked\"})\n            self._log(user_input, meta_events, response=block)\n            return {\n                \"response\": block,\n                \"intercepted\": True,\n                \"scene\": \"CRITICAL\"\n            }\n        \n        # 2. 场景分类 + 元判断"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":57,"aggregated":"=== 3105 pipeline orchestrator ===\n\"\"\"\n主流水线：整合硬拦截、分类（含元判断）、模板注入、LLM调用、后置校验、日志记录\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport time\nimport uuid\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 导入各模块\nfrom interceptors.critical_interceptor import critical_intercept\nfrom templates.template_map import TEMPLATE_MAP\n\n# 尝试加载模型分类器，失败则用规则分类器\nSCENE_CLASSIFIER_DIR = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\nMODEL_PATH = os.path.join(SCENE_CLASSIFIER_DIR, \"models/scene_classifier.pkl\")\n\ntry:\n    os.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n    from classifier.scene_classifier import SceneClassifier\n    classifier = SceneClassifier.load(MODEL_PATH)\n    print(f\"Loaded embedding classifier from {MODEL_PATH}\")\nexcept (ImportError, FileNotFoundError) as e:\n    print(f\"Using rule-based fallback classifier: {e}\")\n    from classifier.rule_classifier import RuleClassifier\n    classifier = RuleClassifier()\n\n\nclass PipelineOrchestrator:\n    def __init__(self, log_file=None):\n        if log_file is None:\n            # 使用绝对路径\n            base_dir = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\n            log_file = os.path.join(base_dir, \"logs/meta_events.jsonl\")\n        self.log_file = log_file\n        self.llm_call = self._mock_llm  # 可替换为真实LLM调用\n        \n        # 确保日志目录存在\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(log_file) if os.path.dirname(log_file) else \"logs\", exist_ok=True)\n    \n    def process(self, user_input, context=None):\n        \"\"\"\n        处理单次用户输入\n        context: dict，可包含 task_id, history 等\n        \"\"\"\n        meta_events = []\n        response = None\n        \n        # 1. 硬拦截\n        block = critical_intercept(user_input)\n        if block:\n            meta_events.append({\"stage\": \"critical_intercept\", \"action\": \"blocked\"})\n            self._log(user_input, meta_events, response=block)\n            return {\n                \"response\": block,\n                \"intercepted\": True,\n                \"scene\": \"CRITICAL\"\n            }\n        \n        # 2. 场景分类 + 元判断","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080650022}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7f568fa","parentId":"045241df","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:24.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand. The 3105 pipeline:\n1. First checks critical_intercept (hard block)\n2. Then does scene classification (embedding-based or rule-based fallback)\n3. Then generates a response via `_mock_llm` (mock, not real LLM)\n\nSo the `response` field is a template-based text response from `_mock_llm`, not from a real LLM. The classifier is real (KNN or rule-based).\n\nThe `scene` field comes from the KNN classifier or rule classifier. The `confidence` is the similarity score. The `intercepted` is True if the critical interceptor blocked it.\n\nSo the actual format is:- `response`: a text description (template-based)- `scene`: the classified scene label\n\n\n- `confidence`: similarity score (0-1)\n- `intercepted`: boolean\n- `meta`: additional metadata\n\nBut the workspace SKILL.md claims the response has `top_candidates` as the main field. This is completely wrong. The workspace SKILL.md documents the OLD format (from the original v1 design with top_candidates), while the actual 3105 returns the v2 format (response+scene+confidence+intercepted+meta). The `top_candidates` format doesn't exist anymore.\n\nSo the SKILL.md at workspace/skills/v8_classifier is documenting a non-existent API format. This is a documentation bug.\n\nI need to fix this because agents reading the SKILL.md will think the 3105 API returns `top_candidates` when it actually doesn't. The auto-score-classify hook only uses `scene` and `intercepted` anyway, so it's not affected, but the documentation is still wrong.\n\nLet me fix the SKILL.md to match the actual 3105 response format.","thinkingSignature":"aa0464e3330c1970eef35dba721cec74954ca6d6c1f2e34f4085a48dfe5ab5df"},{"type":"text","text":"发现 **SKILL.md 文档和实际 API 格式完全不匹配**：\n\n```\nworkspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md 声称：\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.73], ...]\n  scene 字段不存在\n\n实际 3105 返回（PipelineOrchestrator）：\n  response: \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入...\"\n  scene: \"clarify\"\n  confidence: 0.62\n  intercepted: false\n  meta: \"ambiguous\"\n```\n\n这是 P0 级文档 bug——任何读 SKILL.md 的 agent 都会学到错误的 API 格式。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vyiqvk90dc4p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 查看完整 3105 响应结构 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写个备份脚本\"}' | python3 -m json.tool"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102387,"output":569,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121851,"cost":{"input":0.0307161,"output":0.0006828,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0325326}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080650037,"responseId":"062c0a0ac13b008e81d22477900f83d9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dfa61db","parentId":"e7f568fa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:24.881Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vyiqvk90dc4p_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 查看完整 3105 响应结构 ===\n{\n    \"response\": \"[LLM\\u54cd\\u5e94] \\u57fa\\u4e8e\\u4f60\\u7684\\u8f93\\u5165\\uff0c\\u5efa\\u8bae\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u5982\\u4e0b\\uff1a...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.5324037075042725\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":94,"aggregated":"=== 查看完整 3105 响应结构 ===\n{\n    \"response\": \"[LLM\\u54cd\\u5e94] \\u57fa\\u4e8e\\u4f60\\u7684\\u8f93\\u5165\\uff0c\\u5efa\\u8bae\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u5982\\u4e0b\\uff1a...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n    \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.5324037075042725\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080664871}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bdd8d4a","parentId":"2dfa61db","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:28.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to fix the workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md to match the actual 3105 response format. The SKILL.md needs to be updated to reflect the actual response fields.Let me check the full workspace SKILL.md to understand what needs to change.","thinkingSignature":"9127c01e76016d1c9903afb9354fd8539a71fdb3115f38142ba579460d08b2d3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jpes07tpegl5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103091,"output":112,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122098,"cost":{"input":0.030927299999999998,"output":0.0001344,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0321954}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080664885,"responseId":"062c0a17ec77e04f771b6ac75ff792b0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10f159cd","parentId":"6bdd8d4a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:28.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jpes07tpegl5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n> 置信度 = 1 - cosine_distance，即与最近邻的相似度（0-1，1 表示完全匹配）\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 相似度 < 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 相似度差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n[223 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080668484}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e8e37c7","parentId":"10f159cd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:33.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to fix the SKILL.md to match the actual 3105 response. The response format is:\n```\n{\n  \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n  \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.5324037075042725\n}\n```\n\nLet me read the rest of the SKILL.md to understand what needs to change.","thinkingSignature":"561681596e7c38b9c85f9e03cdcd17f9720e501211b211f7f56d03f3f041e028"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s61wgzv1xyln_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","offset":51,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103822,"output":162,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122879,"cost":{"input":0.0311466,"output":0.00019439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0324747}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776080668501,"responseId":"062c0a1b5b639bfc5bdd34ebb8c281e7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae3a087c","parentId":"3e8e37c7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:44:33.466Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s61wgzv1xyln_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n[143 more lines in file. Use offset=131 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776080673456}}
