{"type":"message","id":"eadf064d","parentId":"c07ae066","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:59:16.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4gf5c2dhf9w4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776081556856}}
{"type":"message","id":"66439416","parentId":"eadf064d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:59:22.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the exec works but the for loop might be hanging. Let me try a simpler approach with a single find command.","thinkingSignature":"6aaad1b73a091e66905f76e464aeb16bb8cc8a59440e1861d0988ddc4809ff0b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zcmhp7tfoakf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills -name \"SKILL.md\" -exec sh -c 'echo \"$(basename $(dirname {})): $(grep -m1 description: {} | cut -c14-)\"' \\; 2>/dev/null | sort"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61828,"output":108,"cacheRead":18895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80831,"cost":{"input":0.0185484,"output":0.0001296,"cacheRead":0.0011336999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0198117}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776081556868,"responseId":"062c0d943344b411d6cc73286fa20c94"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0fbab7d1","parentId":"66439416","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:59:22.234Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zcmhp7tfoakf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"agent-team-orchestration: \"Orchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\"\nautomation-workflows: Design and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on \"automate\", \"automation\", \"workflow automation\", \"save time\", \"reduce manual work\", \"automate my business\", \"no-code automation\".\nclassifier-health: 分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\nclaude-code-architecture: \nclaude-code-commands: : string\nclaude-code-security: \nclaude-code-telemetry: \nclaude-code-tools: \ncritical-interceptor: \nelite-longterm-memory: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\ngithub-manager: \nintent-enhancer: 增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\nmemory-keeper: \nmulti-search-engine: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\nontology: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\nproactivity: Anticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\nproductivity-automation-kit: \"效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\"\nscene-classifier: \nscrapling: \nself-improving: \"Self-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when (1) a command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2) the user corrects you or rejects your work; (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated or incorrect; (4) you discover a better approach; (5) the user explicitly installs or references the skill for the current task.\"\nskill-vetter: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\nsuperpowers: Spec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow.\ntask_orchestrator: \nv8_classifier: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nv8_scorer: OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎。调用 3103 API，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略。用于判断用户任务应走 DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA 哪种执行路径。\nvercel-deploy: Deploy and manage Vercel projects. Use when deploying applications to Vercel, managing environment variables, checking deployment status, viewing logs."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":157,"aggregated":"agent-team-orchestration: \"Orchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\"\nautomation-workflows: Design and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on \"automate\", \"automation\", \"workflow automation\", \"save time\", \"reduce manual work\", \"automate my business\", \"no-code automation\".\nclassifier-health: 分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\nclaude-code-architecture: \nclaude-code-commands: : string\nclaude-code-security: \nclaude-code-telemetry: \nclaude-code-tools: \ncritical-interceptor: \nelite-longterm-memory: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\ngithub-manager: \nintent-enhancer: 增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\nmemory-keeper: \nmulti-search-engine: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\nontology: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\nproactivity: Anticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\nproductivity-automation-kit: \"效率自